quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,‘Kâf. Nge’Kur’ân eZukileyo
  50,2,"Ke kaloku bamangaliseka kukuba kufike uMlumkisi kubo ephuma phakathi kwabo, yaye abangakholwayo bathi: “Yinto engumnqa le"
  50,3,"Sisakuba sifile sele siluthuli, (siza kuphinda sibuyiselwe ebomini)? Oko kukubuyela (emhlabeni) okukude.”"
  50,4,"Siyakwazi okwabo okugqitywa ngumhlaba, yaye kuThi kukho iNcwadi elondoloziweyo"
  50,5,Kodwa bona bayiphikile inyaniso isakuba ifikile kubo. Ngoko ke bakwimo yokudideka
  50,6,"Abajonganga na ezulwini ngentla kwabo ukuba Salakha njani, Salihombisa nokulihombisa kwanokuba kukanjani na ukungabi nazintanda kwalo"
  50,7,Kanti nomhlaba Siwandlalile Sabeka iintaba ezimile ngokuqinileyo Senza kwahluma apho kuwo (umhlaba) neentlobo zezinto ezintle
  50,8,"Ezinika ukhanyiselo, nesikhumbuzi kuye wonke osisicaka esibuyelayo (kuAllâh)"
  50,9,Kananjalo Sithobe imvula esikelelekileyo isuka esibhakabhakeni Senza ngayo kwahluma izitiya neenkozo ezivela kwisivuno
  50,10,Nemithi emide yesundu ineziqhamo ezicwangciswe ngokwemiqolo eyalekeneyo
  50,11,"Umsindleko wezicaka (zika-Allâh), kananjalo Sinike ubomi ngayo (imvula) emhlabeni ofileyo. Lunjalo ke uvuko (lwabafileyo)"
  50,12,Abantu bakwaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo nabemi baseRassi1 nabakwaThamûd
  50,13,Nabakwa-’Ad nabakwaFir’awn nabazalwana bakaLût
  50,14,"Nabemi basezinkunini nabantu baseTubba’, ngamnye kubo wamphika uMthunywa wabo, saza isilumkiso saM sehla (phezu kwabo) ke"
  50,15,Ingaba Sasilela kwindalo yokuqala kusini na? Kodwa basekudidekeni ngokuphathelene nendalo entsha
  50,16,Ke kaloku Samdala umntu yaye Siyakwazi okusetyezwa ngumphefumlo wakhe kuye. Kwaye Thina Sisondele kuye kunomthovutho2 wakhe
  50,17,Xa abamkeli3 ababini besamkela behleli ekunene nasekhohlo
  50,18,Akukho nalinye ilizwi umntu alithethayo koko kuba sele kukho umqwalaseli osele elungele (ukubhala)
  50,19,Kananjalo ukuyoba kokufa kuya kuza nenyaniso; ebenizama ukuyiphepha
  50,20,Ke kaloku neXilongo liya kuvuthelwa. Leyo iya kuba iyiMini isilumkiso sasikhutshiwe (ngayo)
  50,21,Umphefumlo ngamnye uya kuza nomqhubi (wawo) nengqina
  50,22,"(Kuya kuthiwa kuwo): “Wena wawungayinanzanga (le Mini), Sisisusile ke isigqubuthelo kuwe, (ngoku) ukubona kwakho naMhlanje kubukhali.”"
  50,23,"Aze umqhubi wawo (ingelosi) athi: “Lo Umbhalo ngulo ukum, sele ulungiswe kakade.”"
  50,24,"(UAllâh Uya kuthi): “Phosa esiHogweni wonke osisingcoli esineenkani ongakholwayo.”"
  50,25,"Uya kuthi uAllâh kulowo ungumoni: “Mthinteli ndini wokulungileyo, mgabadeli ndini, mthandabuzi ndini"
  50,26,"Lowo (walinganisa) thixo bambi noAllâh.” (Aphinde Athi kwingelosi emqhubayo): “Mphose esohlwayweni esibuhlungu.”"
  50,27,"Umhlobo wakhe (uSathana) uya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu, asindim owamenza ukuba abe ngumgabadeli koko nguye ngokwakhe owaba sekulahlekeni (okwambeka) kude.”"
  50,28,"(UAllâh) Uya kuthi: “Musani ukuphikisana phambi kwaM, ekubeni Ndandinilumkisile kwangenxa engaphambili.”"
  50,29,Ilizwi (elingummiselo) aliyi kuguqulwa kuM yaye Andisokuze Ndibe ngumsweli bulungisa kwizicaka
  50,30,"NgeMini eSiya kuthi esiHogweni: “Ingaba ugcwele? Siya (kuphendula) sona sithi: “Ingaba kusekho abanye na?”"
  50,31,"Ke kaloku iPaladesi iya kusondezwa kubenzi bokulungileyo, ingabi kude"
  50,32,"(Kuya kuthiwa): “Oku koko nanithenjiswe ngako (oko) kokwakhe wonke ongumbuyeli kuAllâh nomgcini womnqophiso waKhe"
  50,33,"Owamoyikayo uSozinceba, Ongabonwayo, wabuyela (kuYe) ngentliziyo (enenguquko)"
  50,34,Ngena kuyo (iPaladesi) ngoxolo. Le yiMini yaphakade.”
  50,35,"Baya kufumana konke abakunqwenelayo apho, yaye kuThi kusekho nokunye okungaphaya koko"
  50,36,"Kanti zingaphi izizukulwana eSazitshabalalisayo ngaphambili kunabo, ezazinkulu kunabo ngamandla zityhutyhe ilizwe lonke, ikhona phofu indawo yokubalekela"
  50,37,Inene kuko oko kukho inkumbuzo kuye nabani na ophulaphulayo lo gama ekho (ngokwasengqondweni)
  50,38,Sawadala ngenene amazulu nomhlaba noko kuphakathi kuwo ngeentsuku ezintandathu kwaye akukho kudinwa kwaSichukumisayo
  50,39,"Ke wena yiba nomonde ngoko bakutshoyo, uzukise (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi yakho phambi kokuphuma kwelanga naphambi kokutshona kwalo"
  50,40,(Nakwinxalenye) yobusuku. Mzukise nasemva kokuqubuda (emthandazweni)
  50,41,Ke kaloku uphulaphule ngeMini xa uMmemezi eya kumemeza kwindawo ekufuphi
  50,42,NgeMini abaya kuva isithonga ngenyaniso. Leyo yiMini yokuphuma (emangcwabeni)
  50,43,Inene Sithi abanika ubomi Senze nokufa yaye kuThi kulapho kuza kuphelelwa khona
  50,44,NgeMini umhlaba uya kuzahlukanisa nabo (baze baphume emangcwabeni abo) ngesaquphe; olo luqokelelo olulula kuThi
  50,45,"Sikwazi kakuhle abakuthethayo, yaye wena awungomnyanzelisi phezu kwabo (wokubenza bakholwe ngenkani) kodwa ke wena khumbuza nge’Kur’ân nabani na lowo usoyikayo isilumkiso saM"
  51,1,Ndifunga (ngeMimoya) evuthuzayo
  51,2,(Nangamafu) athwala umthwalo onzima wamanzi
  51,3,Nangee(nqanawa) eziwiza kalula nangocoselelo
  51,4,Nangezo (ngelosi) zahlulahlula (izinto) ngokomyalelo (ka- Allâh)
  51,5,Inene oko nithenjiswe ngako kuyinyaniso
  51,6,Kananjalo inene imbuyekezo iza kwenzeka
  51,7,Ndifunga nangamazulu aneendlela
  51,8,Inene nina nahlukile ngeentetho
  51,9,"Olahlekileyo\twakude\tkuyo\t(i’Kur’ân)\tngulowo ulahlekisiweyo"
  51,10,Abatshabalalayo ngamaxoki
  51,11,Abaphantsi kwesigqubuthelo bengenanyameko
  51,12,"Bayabuza, “Inini na iMini yembuyekezo?”"
  51,13,(Leyo) yiMini abaya kujingiswa ngayo eMlilweni
  51,14,"(Kananjalo kuza kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo senu ke. Oku koko naningenamonde ngako.”"
  51,15,Inene wona amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kweMiyezo nemithombo
  51,16,Esamkela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona. Kaloku wona aye aba ngabenzi bokulungileyo kwangaphambili
  51,17,Wona ayelala kancinane ebusuku
  51,18,Nangeeyure eziphambi konyezi ayeye acele itarhu (kuAllâh)
  51,19,"Kantinasebutyebinibawo(kwakuyekukhutshwe) amalungelo (abahlwempuzekileyo), abangqibi nababandazelekileyo"
  51,20,Ke kaloku emhlabeni kukho imiqondiso kwabanyanisekileyo (elukholweni)
  51,21,Nakuni buqu. Kanti aniboni na
  51,22,Nasezulwini kukho imbonelelo yenu yako konke enithenjiswe ngako
  51,23,"Ke kaloku (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, inene yona (i’Kur’ân) yinyaniso enjengokuba nithetha"
  51,24,Ingaba ibali leendwendwe ezixabisekileyo zikaIbrâhîm lifikile na kuwe
  51,25,"Ekungeneni kwazo emzini wakhe zathi: “(Siya nibulisa) ngoxolo. Waphendula yena, (nakuni makube) luxolo, nina ningabantu abangaziwayo.”"
  51,26,Wahamba waya kusapho lwakhe wabuya nenyama yethole elityetyisiweyo elojiweyo
  51,27,"Walibeka phambi kwazo (iindwendwe ezo); wathi: “Aniyi kutya na?”"
  51,28,"Waziva enokuzoyika. Zathi zona: “Ungoyiki,” zamnika iindaba ezivuyisayo zenkwenkwana enolwazi"
  51,29,"Ke kaloku umkakhe weza kuye ngesikhalo (somothuko) ezibetha ubuso bakhe, esithi: “(Mna ndingumfazi) oludlolwazana nje!”"
  51,30,"Zathi zona: Itsho njalo ke iNkosi yakho; inene yona nguSolubabalo, uSolwazi"
  51,31,"UIbrâhîm wathi: “Myalezo mni na (lo) nize ngawo (apha) kanye kanye nina ziThunywa?”"
  51,32,"Zathi zona: “Inene thina sithunyelwe kubantu abazizaphula- mthetho"
  51,33,Ukuba sithulule phezu kwabo amatye odongwe
  51,34,Aphawulelwe abagabadeli phambi kweNkosi yakho.”
  51,35,Ngoko ke Sakhupha (wonke) olikholwa phakathi apho
  51,36,Kananjalo aSizanga Sifumane mntu ngaphandle komzi omnye wamaMuslim (umzi kaLût neentombi zakhe)
  51,37,Sashiya umqondiso apho kwabo basoyikayo isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  51,38,"Kananjalo kuMûsâ (kwakukho umnqondiso), ukumthumela kweThu kuFir’awn negunya elicacileyo"
  51,39,"Kodwa (uFir’awn) watshikila nabalandeli bakhe, wathi: “(UMûsâ) ngumenzi wemilingo nephambana.”"
  51,40,Samntywilisela elwandle yena namadoda omkhosi wakhe ngenxa yokuba wayesoleka
  51,41,"Nakuma’Ad (wabakhona umnqondiso), xa Sathumela umoya oludlolo1 (owavuthuzayo ngokuchaseneyo nabo)"
  51,42,"Awuzanga usindise nenye into owawubhudla phezu kwayo koko wayishiya itshabalele, ibubutyobo"
  51,43,"NakwaThamûd, xa kwathiwa kubo: “Yibani nizonwabisa okwethutyana.”"
  51,44,"Bona baba nendelelo ngokubhekiselele kumyalelo weNkosi yabo, ngoko iindudumo zabahlasela besajongile"
  51,45,"Azanga bakwazi ukuvuka ke, bengazanga bakwazi nokuzikhusela"
  51,46,"Kananjalo Satshabalalisa abantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili, inene, bona babengabantu, abagabadelayo"
  51,47,"Thina Sawabumba amazulu ngamandla. Inene, Thina Siyakwazi ukwandisa ukwandlaleka kwephakade"
  51,48,"Nomhlaba Siwandlalile, Hayi ubuncutshe boMlungiseleli (wendalo)"
  51,49,Kwizinto zonke Sidale amaqabane (azo) ngambini khona ukuze nikhumbule (iziBele zika-Allâh)
  51,50,Balekelani kuAllâh ke ngoko. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi kuni ocacileyo
  51,51,Musani ukwayamanisa thixo wumbi kuAllâh. Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo kuni
  51,52,"Kwangokunjalo akuzanga khe kufike nawuphi na uMthunywa kwabangaphambili kunabo bangathi: “Umenzi wemilingo okanye iphambana.”"
  51,53,Ingaba babecetyiswe ngabo2 ukuba benze le nto? Nakanye bona buqu bangabantu abagabadela batsiba imida (ekungakholweni)
  51,54,Bayeke ke wena (Muhammad) kuba akuyi kusoleka. (njengoko uwuvakalisile umyalezo kubo)
  51,55,"Bakhumbuze kananjalo, kuba inene inkumbuzo ilulutho kumakholwa"
  51,56,Kananjalo aNdidalanga abantu neeJinni ngaphandle (kokubadalela) ukuba banqule Mna
  51,57,"Andinasixhaso Ndisifunayo kubo, Ndingafuni nakondliwa ngabo Mna"
  51,58,"Inene nguAllâh OnguMondli, uMninimandla amakhulu"
  51,59,Ke kaloku inene okwabo benza ubugwenxa sisabelo (sesohlwayo)esinjengesabelosabahlobobabo(abalandulelayo eli). MabangaNdiqhwayi ngokungenamonde ke
  51,60,Yeha ke kwabo bangakholwayo kwiMini abathenjiswe ngayo
  52,1,(Ndifunga ngeNtaba) yeTûr
  52,2,NangeNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  52,3,Kumacwecwe avulwe ondlalwa
  52,4,NangoMzi1 ohanjelwa rhoqo
  52,5,Nangophahla (izulu) oluphakamele phezulu
  52,6,Nangolwandle oluzele (ngumlilo)
  52,7,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yakho siza kwenzeka
  52,8,Ngokuba akukho mthinteli (waso)
  52,9,NgeMini izulu liya kuzamazama ngokujikelezayo
  52,10,Neentaba zigqithe zimke
  52,11,Yeha ke ngalooMini kubaphiki
  52,12,Abancokola amampunge bezonwabisa
  52,13,Ngemini abaya kutshovelwa eMlilweni wesiHogo ngamandla
  52,14,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Nangu ke lo Mlilo naniwuphika"
  52,15,"Ngumlingo na lo, okanye aniboni"
  52,16,(Ngenani ke) nitshe phakathi apho; yibani nomonde okanye ningabi namonde kuyafana kuni. Nihlawulwa ngoko nakwenzayo kuphela
  52,17,Inene amalungisa aya kuba semiyezweni naselonwabeni
  52,18,"Esonwabela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona, Ibe neNkosi yawo Iwakhusele esohlwayweni soMlilo wesiHogo"
  52,19,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwabakholwayo): “Yidlani, nisele, naneliseke ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  52,20,"Baya kuba bengqiyamile ezitroneni ezidwelisiweyo, kananjalo Siya kubatshatisa neembelukazi zabafazi abanamehlo amakhulu (amahle)"
  52,21,"Abo baya bakholwa abantwana babo balandela ekhondweni labo ngokholo Siya kubadibanisa nenzala yabo, kwaye aSiyi kubabandeza nto kwizinto zabo. Umntu ngamnye awakusebenzelayo kugciniwe"
  52,22,Kananjalo Siya kubapha iziqhamo nenyama nantoni na abaya kuyinqwenela
  52,23,Baya kunikana indebe (yewayini) apho akuyi kubakho ntetho imbi nakwenziwa kwasono
  52,24,Kuya kuhamba hamba phakathi kwabo (izicaka) ezingamakhwenkwana azele ukulungiselela bona engathi ziiperile ezilondoloziweyo
  52,25,Ke kaloku baya kusondelana babuzane
  52,26,"Baya kuthi: “Inene thina kwixesha elidlulileyo esasikunye nabantu bakuthi ngalo sasisoyika (ukumenza umsindo uAllâh)"
  52,27,"Waza uAllâh Wasibonelela ngobuBele baKhe, Wasikhusela kananjalo kwisohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  52,28,"Inene sasidla ngokucela kuYe ngaphambili. Inene, nguYe OnguMncedi, uSozinceba"
  52,29,Ngoko ke wena (Muhammad) khumbuza kuba wena ngoBabalo lweNkosi yakho akungosiyavumisa okanye umntu ophambeneyo
  52,30,"Okanye bathi (ngawe): “Yimbongi esilindele ukuba ihlelwe lilishwa lexesha”"
  52,31,"Yithi wena: “Lindani kaloku, kuba nam phakathi kwenu ndingomnye wabalindileyo!”"
  52,32,"Makube mhlawumbi ziingqondo zabo ezibayalela ukuba (batsho) obu (buxoki ngawe Muhammad), okanye (bona) bangabantu nje abagabadeleyo"
  52,33,"Okanye bathi: “Uyiqambe ngokwakhe (i’Kur’ân)”? Yeha bona abakholwa"
  52,34,Mabavelise isicengcelezo esifana nayo (i’Kur’ân) kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  52,35,Makube mhlawumbi badalwa ngento engekhoyo? Okanye ngabo abangabadali
  52,36,Makube mhlawumbi ngabo abadala amazulu nomhlaba? Nakanye abaqinisekanga
  52,37,"Makube mhlawumbi banoovimba (bobutyebi) beNkosi yakho, Okanye bangabalawuli babo (oovimba abo)"
  52,38,"Okanye banomchankcatho (wokuya ezulwini) abaphulaphula ngawo (iimfihlelo zezulu)? Ukuba kunnalo, umphulaphuli lowo wabo makaze nobungqina obucacileyo kaloku"
  52,39,Okanye Yena (uAllâh) Uneentombi nibe nina ninoonyana
  52,40,"Okanye wena (Muhammad), ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo myalezo) ukuze bazive besindekile ngumthwalo (wetyala lentlawulo)"
  52,41,"Okanye banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  52,42,Okanye baqulunqa icebo? Kodwa abo bangakholwayo ngabo ekuqulunqwa ngabo
  52,43,OkanyebanomnyeuthixoongaphandlekoAllâh?Makazukiswe uAllâh Ongentla kwayo yonke into abayayamanisa naYe
  52,44,"Ke kaloku xa benokubona iceba lisiwa livela esibhakabhakeni bangathi: “Ngamafu (njee) ayinqumba!”"
  52,45,Bayeke ke wena bade badibane neMini yabo abaya kubethwa bengaqondi
  52,46,"Mini leyo icebo labo lingayi kubanceda nto, bengayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa"
  52,47,Inene kwabo benze ubugwenxa sisohlwayo esingaphambili kunoku kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi
  52,48,"Ke kaloku wena (Muhammad) yiba nomonde ngesigqibo senkosi yakho kuba inene wena usemehlweni eThu, kananjalo zukisa (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi, yakho xa uvuka"
  52,49,Nangenxalenye yobusuku Mzukise Yena nasemva (kokutshona) kweenkwenkwezi
  53,1,(Ndifunga) ngenkwenkwezi xa isihla
  53,2,Ugxa wenu (uMuhammad) akalahlekanga yaye akenzanga mpazamo
  53,3,Engathethi okomnqweno wakhe
  53,4,Asinto yimbi (le ‘Kur’ân) ngaphandle kokuba sisiTyhilelo esityhiliweyo
  53,5,Ufundiswe ngonamandla amakhulu (uJibrîl)
  53,6,"Ongenasiphene, yena waphakama waba ngemo yakhe yokwenene"
  53,7,Lo gama waye kwindawo ephakamileyo yolundi
  53,8,"Weza, wehla phantsi"
  53,9,Waba kumgama ongangobude bezaphetha ezibini okanye nganeno (kunoko)
  53,10,Watyhila (uJibrîl) kwisicaka saKhe (uAllâh) awakutyhilayo
  53,11,Intliziyo (ingqondo) ayizanga ixoke ngoko yakubonayo
  53,12,Niza kumphikisa na nina ngoko wakubonayo
  53,13,"Kananjalo\twambona\tyena\t(uMuhammad)\tngenene kwisihlandlo sesibini"
  53,14,NgakwiSidratul Muntaha
  53,15,"Kufutshane\tnayo\t(iSidratul\tMuntaha)\tkukho\tumyezo wokhuseleko (iPaladesi)"
  53,16,Yabona wathi usakugqunywa uMthi womLote yiloo nto yayiwugqumile
  53,17,Amehlo (OMprofeti uMuhammad) akalaqaza (ajonge kwenye indawo) engazanga agabadele
  53,18,Yena (wayibona ngenene eyona miqondiso mikhulu yeNkosi yakhe)
  53,19,Ke (nina) nibajongile na ooAl- Lat- noAl ‘Uzzâ
  53,20,"NoManât, ongowesithathu kubo"
  53,21,Ingaba okwenu ngabesiduna na ize kuYe ibe ngabesikhomokazi
  53,22,Oko ke (ukuba kunjalo) kukwaba okungenabulungisa
  53,23,"(Lawo) akanto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ngamagama (njee) eniziqambele ngokwenu nina kunye nookhokho benu (magama lawo) uAllâh Angathumelanga gunya (ngawo) Abalandeli nto ngaphandle koqash-qash noko kunqwenelwa yimiphefumlo yabo, ukanti sele sifikile kubo isiKhokelo esivela eNkosini yabo"
  53,24,Ingaba umntu unako (konke) akunqwenelayo
  53,25,Kodwa uBomi belizayo bobuka-Allah nobokuqala
  53,26,Zingaphi iingelosi ezisezulwini ezintethelelo yazo ingayi kunceda nto ngaphandle kokuba uAllâh Ade Anike imvume kulowo Athande ukumnika namamkeleyo
  53,27,Inene abo bangakholwayo kuBomi oBuzayo bathiya iingelosi amagama esikhomokazi
  53,28,"Yaye malunga noko abanalwazi, akukho nto balandela yona ngaphandle koqash qash, inene, uqash-qash akancedi nto ngokuchasene nenyaniso"
  53,29,Wena zikhwebule kulowo utshikilela umyalezo weThu ongafuni nto ngaphandle kobomi beli hlabathi
  53,30,"Lowo ngumyinge wolwazi lwabo, inene iNkosi yakho yiYona, Yaziyo okokuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, ikwayiYo kananjalo Eyaziyo ukuba ngubani na okuso isiKhokelo"
  53,31,"Kananjalo kokuka-Allah okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni khon’ukuze Abuyekeze abo benza ukungcola (ngesohlwayo) ngoko bakwenzayo, Abuyekeze nabo benza okulungileyo (ngomvuzo) omhle"
  53,32,"Abo baziphephayo izono ezikhulu nezenzo ezingcolileyo, benze ezincinane kuphela, inene iNkosi yenu Iphangalele kuxolelo (lwezono), Yona Inazi kakuhle xa Inivelisa4 emhlabeni naxa naniizintsana ezibelekweni zoomama benu. Ngoko ke musani ukubanga ukuba ninyulu, Yena nguYena Waziyo ukuba ngubani na oMoyikayo"
  53,33,"Umbonile na lowo utshikileyo wafulathela, (i-Islam)"
  53,34,Waza wanikela kancinane waphinda wayeka
  53,35,"Ingaba unalo na ulwazi lokungabonwayo, ukuze abone"
  53,36,Akachazelwanga na ngokwakuseziBhalweni zikaMûsâ
  53,37,"NezikaIbrahim, owazalisekisayo"
  53,38,Akukho mthwali wamithwalo uya kuthwaliswa umthwalo womnye
  53,39,Kananjalo akukho nto umntu (aya kuyifumana) ngaphandle kwaleyo wayizabalazelayo
  53,40,Kwaye inene umzamo wakhe uza kubonwa
  53,41,Aze abuyekezwe ngawo ngembuyekezo egcweleyo
  53,42,Kananjalo eNkosini yakho kulapho isiphelo sikhoyo
  53,43,Inene yiYo (iNkosi yakho) Eyenza umntu ahleke aphinde alile
  53,44,IkwayiYo Eyenza ukufa Inike ubomi
  53,45,IkwayiYo Edala abalingane oyindoda nowasetyhini
  53,46,Ngeqabaza lembewu yomntu xa likhutshiwe
  53,47,Kuze (kube yimfuneko) kuYe (ukuba Adale) enye indalo
  53,48,NguYe kananjalo Otyebisayo5 Anelise
  53,49,Kananjalo nguYe iNkosi kaSirius
  53,50,Ukanti Yena Watshabalalisa abantu bokuqala bakwa’Ad
  53,51,NabakwaThamûd nabo Akazanga Abasindise
  53,52,Nabantu bakwaNûh ngaphambili. Inene yayingabo abaya ababi nabulungisa baba ngabacinezeli
  53,53,"Ke\tkaloku\tWazitshabalalisa\tizixeko\tezabhedululwayo Wazikhahlela phantsi"
  53,54,Wabagqumelela ngoko Wabagqumelela ngako
  53,55,ZiziphinakeezintsikelelozeNkosiyenuniyakuzithandabuza
  53,56,"Lo\t(Mprofeti)\tnguMlumkisi\tnjengabanye\tabaLumkisi bamandulo"
  53,57,IMini esondelayo isondele (yona)
  53,58,"Mayela\tnayo\takukho\tbani\tngaphandle\tkoAllâh Onokuyishenxisa"
  53,59,Ingaba le ntetho iyanimangalisa kusini na
  53,60,Ke kaloku nina niyahleka anilili
  53,61,Nibe nisadlalisa ngokuzonwabisa
  53,62,Qubudani ke nina (maMuslim) kuAllâh niMnqule. (Yena Yedwa)
  54,1,IYure sele ifikile yaye nenyanga sele icandeke (kubini)
  54,2,"Ke kaloku xa bebona umqondiso (ummangaliso), bayatshikila bathi: “(Lo) ngumlingo ogqithayo.”"
  54,3,"Kananjalo baye baphika, balandela iminqweno yabo. Kodwa into nganye inexesha lokufezekiswa (kwayo)"
  54,4,Ke kaloku sele ifikile kubo inkcazelo ekukho kuyo isilumkiso (esaneleyo ngokubhekiselele kugabadelo)
  54,5,Ubulumko obuphangaleleyo kodwa isilumkiso asibancedi (nto)
  54,6,"Bayeke ke (Muhammad), ngeMini uMkhwazi aya kubizela abantu kwinto engathandekiyo (uMlilo wesiHogo)"
  54,7,"Amehlo abo aya kuba ethobekile, baya kuphuma emangcwabeni wabo bengathi ziinkumbi bethe saa"
  54,8,"Begxalathelana besiya phambili kuMkhwazi. Abangakholwayo baya kuthi: “Le yiMini enzima.”"
  54,9,"Abantu bakaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo, ke kaloku basiphika isiCaka seThu. Bathi: “ (Lo uNûh) yindoda ephambanayo” wada (uNûh) wagxothwa (ngabo)"
  54,10,"Ke kaloko wacela eNkosini yakhe: “Inene mna ndoyisakele, ndincede ke Wena (Nkosi yam).”"
  54,11,Thina ke Savula iingcango zezulu nemvula eyathululeka phantsi
  54,12,"Eyenza umhlaba wagqabhuka yimithombo namanzi, aza namanzi adibana nento eyayisele imiselwe kakade"
  54,13,Samthumela ke yena (ngenqanawa eyenziwe) ngamaplanga nezikhonkwane
  54,14,Idada phantsi kolondolozo lweThu njengomvuzo kulowo wayephikiwe (uNûh)
  54,15,"Sayishiya\tukuba\tibe\tngumqondiso1,\tukhona\tke\toza kukhumbula (okanye afumane isilumkiso)"
  54,16,Saba njani ke ukuba (buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,17,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,18,Ama’Ad aphika; saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,19,"Inene, Thina Sathumela kubo umoya otswinayo ngemini eyayiyeyeshwangusha (elalisihla emva kweshwangusha)"
  54,20,Lincothula abantu ngokungathi zizibhukubhuku zemithi yesundu encothulwe neengcambu
  54,21,Saba njani (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,22,"Kananjalo Siyenze yalula i’Kur’ân ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,23,AmaThamûd asala isilumkiso
  54,24,"Athi:“Ingabangumntuomnyephakathikwethuesizakulandela yena? Inene singaba sekulahlekeni nasempambanweni"
  54,25,Ingaba umyalezo uthunyelwe kuye phakathi kwethu? Hayi khona lixoki elingenazintloni (lo)!”
  54,26,"Baza\tkumazi\tngomso\tukuba\tngubani\tna\tolixoki elingenazintloni"
  54,27,"Inene Thina Sithumele ithokazi lenkamela ukuba libe luvavanyo kubo, bajonge ke ube nomonde"
  54,28,"Ubaxelele kananjalo okokuba amanzi baza kwahlulelana ngawo, (Nenkamela), ngenye (imini) kuza kusela bona (ize ibe yinkamela ngenye imini)"
  54,29,"Kodwa bona babiza ugxa wabo2, waba nesibindi wayinqumla imisipha"
  54,30,Saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) iSohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,31,Inene Thina Sathoba isiqhushumbisi phezu kwabo baba ngathi ziintsasa ezomileyo ezizizijungqu zesibaya sezilwanyana
  54,32,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,33,Abantu bakwaLût basala isilumkiso
  54,34,"Inene, Thina Sathumela isiphango samatye phezu kwabo ngaphandle kosapho lukaLût, lona Salusindisa phambi koms’obomvu"
  54,35,NgoBabalo oluvela kuThi. Simvuza kanjalo ke onombulelo
  54,36,"Ke kaloku yena wayesele ebalumkisile (kwantlandlolo) ngohlaselo lweThu, kodwa bona basiphikisa isilumkiso"
  54,37,"Kananjalo bafuna ukuxhwila iindwendwe zakhe, Kodwa Sabamfamekisela amehlo abo (SiSithi): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,38,Ke kaloku ekuseni bafikelwa sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  54,39,"(Kwathiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,40,Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke kodwa ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula
  54,41,Kanti nakubantu bakwaFir’awn kwafika isilumkiso
  54,42,"Bayala imiqondiso yeThu yonke, Sabahlasela ke ngohlaselo lwaloWo Unobunganga, Unamandla"
  54,43,"Ingaba (abantu) abangakholwayo benu bangcono kunabayaa bamandulo, okanye ninogonyo oluvela kwiziBhalo"
  54,44,"Okanye bathi: “Thina silibandla elixhasanayo,” kusini na"
  54,45,"(Elo) bandlana labo liza koyiswa, kwaye baza kuza ngemiva (babaleke)"
  54,46,"Kodwa iYure lixesha labo elimisiweyo, kwaye iYure leyo ingaphaya ngokonakalisa yaye ikrakra ngakumbi"
  54,47,Inene izaphula-mthetho zisekulahlekeni nasempambanweni
  54,48,"NgeMini abaya kurhuqelwa eMlilweni ngobuso babo kuya (kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ukuchukunyiswa sisiHogo kaloku”"
  54,49,Inene Sidale zonke izinto ngommiselo (wento eziya kuba yiyo)
  54,50,"Ukanti\tumyalelo\tweThu\tuba\tmnye\tjwi\tube\tngathi kukuqhwanyaza kweliso"
  54,51,"Kananjalo Sele Sabatshabalalisa abanjengani, ukhona phofu za kukhumbula"
  54,52,Kananjalo yonke into abayenzayo ibhaliwe emacwecweni
  54,53,Kwaye nto nganye encinane (nenkulu) ibhaliwe
  54,54,Inene amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kwemiyezo nemilambo
  54,55,"Esihlalweni sentlonipheko ecaleni kukaSobunganga, uSomandla"
  55,1,USolubabalo
  55,2,Wafundisa i’Kur’ân
  55,3,Wadala umntu
  55,4,Wamfundisa ukuthetha
  55,5,"Ilanga\tnenyanga\tzijikeleza\tngokwemilinganiselo echanekileyo (ezibalelwe yona)"
  55,6,Neenkwenkwezi nemithi ziyaqubuda
  55,7,Nezulu Waliphakamisa walinyanzela ukuzinza
  55,8,Khon’ukuze ningayigabadeli imida ebekiweyo
  55,9,Kwanokuba nijongisise nimete (izinto) ngokulinganayo ningenzi umlinganiselo ube nesikhwasilima
  55,10,"Kanti\tnomhlaba\tUwubeke\tphantsi\t(Wawandlalela) izilwanyana"
  55,11,"Apho kuwo kukho iziqhamo, iidatilisi zesundu ezivelisa amakhasi"
  55,12,"neenkozo kananjalo ezinamagqabi efula, nezityalo ezinuka kamnandi"
  55,13,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,14,Wadala umntu ngodongwe lokwenyani olunjengodongwe lomxonxi
  55,15,Ukanti zona iijinni Wazidala ngedangatya lomlilo ongenamsi
  55,16,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,17,"(Yena) yiNkosi yazo zombini iiMpumalanga, EkwayiNkosi yazo zombini iiNtshonalanga"
  55,18,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,19,Yena Wakhulula iilwandle ezimbini1 ukuba zidibane
  55,20,"Phakathi kwazo kukho umsantsa, alukho olutsiba umda kuwo (ezi lwandle zimbini)"
  55,21,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,22,Kuzo zombini (ezi lwandle) kuphuma iiperile neekorale
  55,23,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,24,Kananjalo zezaKhe iinqanawa eziye (zibonakale) ziphakamile elwandle ngathi ziintaba
  55,25,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,26,Wonke ubani kuwo (umhlaba) uza kutshabalala
  55,27,Kuze kusale uBuso2 beNkosi yakho uMnini bungangamsha nozuko
  55,28,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,29,"Wonke osemazulwini nasemhlabeni ucela kuYe; imihla yonke, Yena Uba nento Akuyo (Ayenzayo)"
  55,30,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,31,"Siza\tkunihoya\tnina\tzidalwa\tzibini\t(iiJinni\tnabantu) zixhomekeke (kuThi)"
  55,32,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,33,"Hini na bandla ndini leejinni nabantu, ukuba niye naba nako ukugqitha ngaphaya kwemimandla yezulu nomhlaba gqithani ke. Aniyi kugqitha ngaphandle kwegunya (elivela kuAllâh)"
  55,34,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,35,Kuya kuthunyelwa kuni amadangatya omlilo nomsi yaye aniyi kuzikhusela
  55,36,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,37,"Ke kaloku lakucandeka izulu, livuleke, libe ngathi yirozi ebomvu okwe-oli"
  55,38,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,39,Ngaloo Mini akukho namnye oza kubuzwa ngesono sakhe phakathi koluntu neejinni (kuba abenzi bezono nabalungileyo baya kuzicacela ngaloo Mini)
  55,40,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,41,"Izaphula-mthetho ziya kubonakala ngeempawu zazo, yaye ziya kuxhakamfulwa ngeenyawo (zazo)"
  55,42,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,43,Nasi ke isiHogo ebesiphikwa zizaphula-mthetho
  55,44,Baya kujikeleza phakathi kwaso namanzi atshisayo enziwe ashushu (kanobom)
  55,45,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,46,"Ke yena lowo waye woyika ukumiswa (phambi) kweNkosi yakhe, uya kuba neMiyezo emibini"
  55,47,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,48,(IMiyezo le yo) iya kuba namasebe (athe saa)
  55,49,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,50,Kuyo yomibini (iMiyezo leyo) kuya kubakho imithombo empompozayo
  55,51,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,52,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho zonke iziqhamo zeentlobo ezimbini
  55,53,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,54,"Bengqengqe kwiimandlalo zabo eziqukunjelwe ngesilika enzima, iziqhamo zemiyezo emibini zona zijingela phantsi (kufutshane)"
  55,55,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,56,"(Kuloo miyezo) kuya kubakho abafazi abaya kuba bekrwaqula ngokuzibambileyo, abangazanga bachukunyiswe ndoda najinni ngaphambili"
  55,57,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,58,Ngokungengathi ziiRubhi neekorale
  55,59,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,60,Ingaba ukhona na umvuzo wokulungileyo ngaphezulu kokulungileyo na
  55,61,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,62,Ngezantsi kwayo yomibini (iMiyezo leyo) kuya kubakho eminye iMiyezo emibini
  55,63,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,64,Iya kuba luhlaza yaka (ngokwebala)
  55,65,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,66,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho imithombo emibini etsawulayo
  55,67,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,68,Kuyo yomibini kuya kubakho iziqhamo nemithi yesundu nerharnathi
  55,69,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,70,"Kuyo kuya kubakho abafazi abalungileyo, abahle"
  55,71,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,72,"Abaziimbelukazi\teziya\tkujezula\tngokuzibambileyo, eminqubeni emihle"
  55,73,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,74,Ezingazanga zachukunyiswa ngumntu najinni ngaphambili
  55,75,Ziziphi ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,76,Zithe zava kwizihlalo ezitofotofo eziluhlaza neenkukho ezintle
  55,77,Ziziphi na ke ezi ntsikelelo zeNkosi yenu niya kuziphika
  55,78,"Lisikelelekile igama leNkosi yakho, uMnini bungangamsha nozuko"
  56,1,Xa isehlo sisihla
  56,2,Ekuhleni kwaso akukho kuphika
  56,3,Siya kuthobisela abanye sinyusele abanye
  56,4,Xa umhlaba ushukuma ngokudlokova
  56,5,Neentaba zidiliziwe zaluthuli
  56,6,Zaba luthuli oluphaphathekayo
  56,7,Nize nina nibe ziindidi ezintathu
  56,8,Ke kaloku amadlelane angasekunene; ziintoni na amadlelane angasekunene
  56,9,"Namadlelane\tangasekhohlo;\tziintoni\tna\tamadlelane angasekhohlo"
  56,10,Nabanduleli; abanduleli (bona)
  56,11,Abo ngabo basondezwe kufutshane (noAllâh)
  56,12,EMiyezweni yolonwabo
  56,13,Neqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamandulo
  56,14,Nabambalwa (bezizukulwana) zamva
  56,15,(Baya kuba) sezitroneni eziqukunjelwe (ngezihombiso)
  56,16,"Behleli zava kuzo, bejongene ubuso ngobuso"
  56,17,Kuya kujikeleza phakathi kwabo amakhwenkwe enzelwe (ukuphila) ngonaphakade
  56,18,"Nezitya, imiphanda nendebe (yewayini) ephuma kumthombo ompompozayo"
  56,19,"Akukho kuqaqamba kwantloko baya kuba nako apho, bengayi kunxila nakunxila"
  56,20,Neziqhamo baya kuzikhethela
  56,21,Nenyama yentaka abathe bayinqwenela
  56,22,Neembelukazi (zabafazi) abanamehlo abanzi (amahle)
  56,23,Abafana neeperile ezilondolozwe ngononophelo
  56,24,Njengomvuzo woko bakusebenzelayo
  56,25,Abayi kuva ntetho ingcolileyo nakwenziwa kwasono apho
  56,26,"Kuphela (abaya kukuva) iya kuba: “(Makube) luxolo.”"
  56,27,"Amadlelane\tangasekunene;\tyintoni\tamadlelane angasekunene"
  56,28,"(Baya kuba) phakathi kwemithi yoMlote, engenameva"
  56,29,Nemithi yebhanana (eneziqhamo) ezalekeneyo
  56,30,Nomthuzi owandisiweyo
  56,31,Namanzi ampompozayo
  56,32,Neziqhamo ezininzi
  56,33,Ezinganqamkiyo (ukuntshula) zingalelwanga nokwalelwa (ukuba zityiwe)
  56,34,Nakwiimandlalo eziphakanyiselwe phezulu
  56,35,Inene Thina Sibavelisele (abafazi bePaladesi) kwindalo (entsha)
  56,36,Sabenza baziintombi (ezingazani nandoda)
  56,37,Ezizinikeleyo (kubayeni bazo) zinobudala obulinganayo
  56,38,Izezamadlelane angasekunene
  56,39,Aliqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamandulo
  56,40,Neqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamva
  56,41,Neqela lamadlelane angasekhohlo yintoni na amadlelane angasekhohlo
  56,42,"(Baya\tkuba)\tseMlilweni\totshisayo\tnamanzi\tashushu (kanobom)"
  56,43,Nethinzi lomsi omnyama thsuh
  56,44,Elingapholanga lingancedi nakunceda
  56,45,Inene bona kaloku bazanelisa ngobutyebi ngaphambili
  56,46,Kananjalo bona babethe gqolo ngokugabadela (ngezono ezikhulu)
  56,47,"Kwaye babesithi: “Xa sele sifile saba luthuli namathambo, siza kuphinda ngenene sivuswe"
  56,48,Nookhokho bethu nabo ngokunjalo?”
  56,49,"Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Inene abantu bokuqala nabantu bokugqibela"
  56,50,Baza kuqokelelelwa iMini ekhethiweyo.”
  56,51,Ke kaloku nina ndawonye nabo balahlekileyo baphikayo
  56,52,Niya kutyiswa umthi weZa’kkûm
  56,53,Nizalise izisu zenu ngawo
  56,54,Niphinde ngaphezu koko nisezwe amanzi atshisayo
  56,55,Kwaye niya kusela ukusela kweenkamela ezinxaniweyo
  56,56,Iya kuba bububele babo (abaza kubenzelwa) ngoMhla woVuko
  56,57,"Sinidalile nje, kungani na ukuba ningakholwa"
  56,58,Nikubonile phofu oko niye nikukhuphe
  56,59,Nini na abakudalayo nokuba siThi abanguMdali
  56,60,"Simisele ukufa phakathi kwenu, yaye Thina ngeKhe Soyiswe"
  56,61,Kangangokuba Siya kuyiguqula imbonakalo yenu Sinivelise ngenye imo eningayaziyo nina
  56,62,"Ke kaloku sele niyazi indalo yokuqala, aniyi kukhumbula ke"
  56,63,Niyibonile phofu (imbewu) leyo niyityalayo
  56,64,Nini na abayenza ikhule nokuba Sithi abakhulisi
  56,65,Ukuba beSinokuthanda beSingasuka Siyenze yome ibe bubutyobo nihlale nimangazekile
  56,66,"(Nithi): “Inene thina (ngoku) sisematyaleni"
  56,67,Thina sibandazelekile.”
  56,68,Niwabonile phofu amanzi lawo niwaselayo?”
  56,69,Nini na abaza nawo emafini nokuba SiThi abawathobayo
  56,70,"Ukuba beSithanda beSingasuka Siwenze akrakre, kungokuba kutheni ukuba ningabi nambulelo (kuAllâh)"
  56,71,Niwujongile phofu umlilo lowo niwulumekayo
  56,72,Nini na abavelisa umthi wawo nokuba SiThi abaVelisi (bawo)
  56,73,Siwenze wasisikhumbuzi (soMlilo wesiHogo) nembonelelo yabahambi
  56,74,Ngoko ke zukisa igama leNkosi yakho uMnini bukhulu
  56,75,Ke kaloku Mna Ndifunga ngokutshona kweenkwenkwezi
  56,76,Inene esi sisifungo ukuba beniMazi (uMnini) bukhulu
  56,77,Inene yona (le) yi’Kur’ân eZukileyo
  56,78,EseNcwadini ekhuselekileyo
  56,79,"Akukho\tnamnye\toyichukumisayo\tngaphandle kwabahlambulukileyo"
  56,80,IsisiTyhilelo esivela eNkosini yamaphakade
  56,81,Ingaba yintetho eloo lohlobo (le ‘Kur’ân) na le niyiphikayo (nina bangakholwayo)
  56,82,Endaweni (yokubulela uAllâh) ngembonelelo Aninika yona niyaMphika nina
  56,83,Kutheni xa umphefumlo (womntu ofayo) ufikelela emqaleni (ningangeneleli) kaloku
  56,84,Ukusuka apho nina ngeloo lixa (nisuka nime) nijonge
  56,85,Thina ke Siba Sikufutshane kuye kunani kodwa nina nibe ningaboni
  56,86,Kutheni kaloku (nisima nijonge ningamncedi nje) xa ngaba anizozicaka (kuThi)
  56,87,Ningambuyiseli nje (ebomini kwakhona) ukuba ninenyaniso
  56,88,Ke kaloku ukuba yena (umfi lowo) ube engomnye wabo basondeleyo kuAllâh (ngokuthandwa)
  56,89,"Okwakhe\tiya\tkuba\tkukuphumla\t(ngoxolo)\tnoBubele noMyezo wolonwabo"
  56,90,Kanti ukuba ube engomnye wamadlelane wabangasekunene
  56,91,"(Iingelosi ziya kuthi kuye): “Makube lukhuseleko noxolo kuwe wena oluvela kumadlelane angasekunene.”"
  56,92,"Kodwa ukuba ube engomnye wabaphiki, abalahlekileyo"
  56,93,Okwakhe lowo kukubelezelelwa ngamanzi atshisayo
  56,94,Nokutsha eMlilweni wesiHogo
  56,95,Inene le yinyaniso yoqobo
  56,96,"Zukisa igama leNkosi yakho, uMnini bungangamsha"
  57,1,"Yonke into esemazulwini nasemhlabeni izukisa uAllâh, Yena nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  57,2,"LolwaKhe ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba, Unika ubomi, Enze ukufa. Kananjalo Yena Unamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  57,3,"Yena ngowokuQala ngowokuGqibela, Ungentla, yaye Ukufutshane, kananjalo nguMazi wezinto zonke"
  57,4,"NguYe Owadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeentsuku ezintandathu, waza Wanyukela ngentla kweTrone, Uyakwazi okungena emhlabeni nokuphuma kuwo, nokuhlayo kuvela ezulwini nokunyukela kulo kwaye Yena Ukunye nani naphi na apho nikhoyo, kananjalo uAllâh Uyakwazi enikwenzayo"
  57,5,Yena lulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba. Kananjalo kukuAllâh apho (zonke) izinto zibuyela khona
  57,6,"Yena Wenza ubusuku bungene kwimini, Enze imini ingene kubusuku, Yaye nguMazi wokusezifubeni"
  57,7,"Kholwani ke kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, ninikele kumalizo ngoko Anenze naba ziindlalifa zako. Ngokuba abo bakholiweyo phakathi kwenu baze banikele kumalizo baya kuba nomvuzo omkhulu"
  57,8,"Kungani na ukuba ningakholwa kuAllâh lo gama uMthunywa enimemela ekukholweni kwiNkosi yenu, ethe kananjalo wathabatha umnqophiso wenu, ukuba ninokuthi nikholwe"
  57,9,"NguYe Othumele iiVesi kwisiCaka saKhe (uMuhammad) ezibubungqina obucacileyo khona ukuze anikhuphe ebumnyameni anifake ekukhanyeni. Inene uAllâh Unobubele, Unenceba kuni"
  57,10,"Kungani na ukuba ninganikeli eNdleleni ka-Allâh lo gama ilifa lamazulu nomhlaba ilelaKhe? Abalingani phakathi kwenu abo banikelayo, balwa nokulwa ngaphambi (koloyiso lwaseMakkah) nabo balwayo (emva kwalo). Abo (balwa ngaphambili) bangentla ngokwebakala kunabo banikela kamva balwa nokulwa. Kodwa uAllâh bonke Ubathembise (ngomvuzo). Kananjalo uAllâh enikwenzayo Uyakwazi"
  57,11,Ngubani (kuni) oya kuboleka uAllâh imboleko elungileyo khon’ukuze (Ayihlawule kuye) ngokuphindaphindiweyo aze ngaphezu koko abe nomvuzo oxabisekileyo
  57,12,"NgeMini eniya kuwabona amakholwa namakholwakazi, ukukhanya kwawo kuwakhokelele ngaphambi kwawo nangasekunene kwawo, (kuya kuthiwa): “Iindaba zovuyo kuni namhlanje zezeMiyezo ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, niya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade Inenene le yimpumelelo enkulu!”"
  57,13,"NgeMini leyo abahanahanisi nabahanahanisikazi baya kuthi kwabo bakholwayo, “Khanisilindeni khon’ukuze sizuze inxalenye yokukhanya kwenu.” Kuya kuthiwa kubo: “Buyelani emva kwenu niye kufuna ukukhanya.” Ke kaloku udonga luya kubekwa phakathi kwabo lunocango, umphakathi walo unenceba, kodwa umphandle walo usisohlwayo"
  57,14,"Bona (abahanahanisi) baya kukhwaza (abakholwayo) bathi: “Sasingekunyanga nani na?” Abakholwayo baya kuthi: “Ewe, kodwa nina nazithuthumbisa ngokwenu, nilindele (ilishwa phezu kwethu1) neengcinga zeminqweno yenu zanimfamekisa kwada kwafika umyalelo ka-Allâh. Kwaye umkhohlisi (uSathana) wanikhohlisa ngoAllâh"
  57,15,"Namhlanje ke akukho ntlawuliso yakuzikhulula iya kwamkelwa kuni nakwabo bangakholwayo. Ikhaya lenu nguMlilo, yiyona nto inifanele kakhulu (leyo). Aliselibi ngako ikhaya lenu lokugqibela"
  57,16,"Alikafiki na ixesha kwabo bakholwayo lokuba iintliziyo zabo zibe nokuzithoba, zizinikele kwinkumbulo ka-Allâh noko kwehlayo kuyinyaniso (i’Kur’ân)? IsiBhalo ngaphambili, kwaza kwathi kwakugqitha ithuba elide kubo iintliziyo zabo (zaqaqadeka) zaba lukhuni, ukanti uninzi lwabo bayadelela, abanantobeko"
  57,17,Yazini into yokuba uAllâh Unika ubomi emhlabeni emva kokungabi nabomi kwawo. Sinicacisele kakuhle imiqondiso hleze niqiqe
  57,18,"Inene amadoda anikelayo ngamalizo, nabasetyhini abanikelayo ngamalizo baboleke uAllâh imboleko elungileyo, iya (kuhlawulwa) ngokuphindeneyo kubo kananjalo baya kuba nomvuzo oxabisekileyo"
  57,19,"Abo bakholwayo kuAllâh nabaThunywa baKhe abo bangabaxhasi benyaniso nabafelukholo, bakunye neNkosi yabo. Okwabo ngumvuzo wabo nokukhanya kwabo kodwa bona abo bangakholwayo, baphika iiVesi zeThu, abo ngamadlelane oMlilo wesiHogo"
  57,20,"Kwazini kananjalo okokuba ubomi balo mhlaba yintlekisa njee nesiphambukisi nobunewunewu nokuqhayiselana nokhuphiswano ekwandiseni ubutyebi nabantwana njengomzekelo wemvula ezityalo zayo zikhula zigcobise umhlwayeli, zisuke zome, ubone sele zijike zamthubi; zisuke zibe bubutyobo obuthe saa. Kanti ke kuBomi oBuzayo sisohlwayo esibuhlungu noxolelo oluvela kuAllâh nokwamkeleka. Buyintoni ubomi basemhlabeni ngaphandle kokuba kukuziqhatha"
  57,21,"Khuphisanani ke ngokufuna ukuxolelwa yiNkosi yenu nomyezo obubanzi bawo bungangobubanzi bamazulu nomhlaba, ulungiselelwe abo bakholwayo kuAllâh nabaThunywa baKhe. Obo bubuBele buka-Allâh Abunika lowo Athande ukumnika, kwaye uAllâh nguMnini buBele oMkhulu"
  57,22,Akukhontlekeleihlayoemhlabeniokanyekuniingabhalwanga phambi kokuba ibekho Inene oko kulula kuAllâh
  57,23,"Khon’ukuze\tningalahli\tithemba\tngoko kuniphosileyo ningakhukhumali kananjalo ngoko Aninike kona. Kwaye uAllâh Akamthandi wonke ozingcayo, noqhayisayo"
  57,24,"(Abo) bangamagogotya bayalela ubugogotya (kwabanye) ke kaloku lowo utshikilayo, inene uAllâh Akananto Ayidingayo, nguSokudunyiswa"
  57,25,"Sele Sabathumela abaThunywa beThu nemiqondiso ecacileyo Sathumela neziBhalo kubo nendlela yokugweba khona ukuze abantu bahlale besebulungiseni. Kananjalo Sathumela2 intsimbi ekukho amandla amakhulu emikhosi kuyo (nezinye izinto) eziyinzuzo eluntwini khon’ukuze uAllâh Enze bacace abo baMxhasayo neziThunywa zaKhe ezingabonwayo. Inene uAllâh Unamandla, Unobunganga"
  57,26,"Kananjalo Sele Sathumela uNûh noIbrâhîm Saza kananjalo Sabeka ubuProfeti neziBhalo kwinzala yabo; yaye phakathi kwayo (inzala yabo leyo) kukho lowo ukhokelelekileyo, kodwa uninzi lwabo alunantobeko konke konke"
  57,27,"Ke kaloku ezinyaweni zabo Sathumela abaThunywa beThu Sabalandelisa ngo’Isâ, unyana kaMaryam, Samnika iVangeli Safaka imfobe nenceba ezintliziyweni zabo balandela yena nokungatshati (ukungatshati) oko baziqambela ngokwabo, Asizanga Sibayalele ngako ngaphandle (kokuzenzela ngokwabo) befuna ukwamkeleka kwako (ukungatshati oko) kuAllâh. Kodwa (ukungatshati oko) azanga bakugcine ngendlela efanelekileyo. Thina ke Sanika abo bakholwayo phakathi kwabo umvuzo wabo kodwa uninzi lwabo alunantobeko konke-konke"
  57,28,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, yoyikani uAllâh nikholwe nakuMthunywa waKhe: Yena Uya kuninika isahlulo esiphindwe kabini kwinceba yaKhe. Anenzele ukukhanya eniya kuhamba ngako Anixolele futhi, ke kaloku uAllâh nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba"
  57,29,(Oku kunjalo) khon’ukuze aBantu beNcwadi (amaYuda namaKhristu) bazi okokuba abanamandla ngokuchasene noBabaloluka-AllâhkwanokubabonkeubuBelebuseSandleni saKhe; Ubunika lowo Athande ukumnika kananjalo uAllâh nguMnini buBele Omkhulu
  58,1,"Inene uAllâh Uyivile intetho yomfazi oxoxa nawe (Muhammad) ngomyeni wakhe, ebhekisa isikhalazo sakhe kuAllâh. Ke kaloku uAllâh Uyayiva incoko yenu, inene uAllâh nguSokuva, nguSokubona"
  58,2,Abo benza idzhihâr1 phakathi kwenu (befuna ukwahlukana) nabafazi babo (abo bafazi babo) abangoonina (ngenyani) Oonina babo ayingabo abanye ngaphandle kwabo babezelwe ngabo. Inene bona bathetha intetho echasekileyo nebubuxoki. Kodwa ke inene Yena uAllâh nguMxoleli Onenceba
  58,3,Kananjalo abo benza idzhihâr kubafazi babo baze baphinde bafune ukubuya umva koko bebekutshilo mabakhulule ikhoboka phambi kokuba bachukumisane nabo kwakhona. Oko koko niyalwa ngako; kwaye uAllâh Ukwazi kakuhle enikwenzayo
  58,4,Ke kaloku lowo ungafumani (khoboka) makazile iinyanga zibe mbini zilandelelana phambi kokuba achukumisane (nomfazi wakhe kwakhona); kananjalo lowo ungakwaziyo (ukuzila) makondle abantu abangamashumi amathandathu abangamahlwempu. Oko kwenzelwe ukuba nikholwe ngokupheleleyo kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe; leyo ke yimiqathango ka-Allâh yaye kwabangakholwayo iya kuba sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  58,5,Inene abo baphikisa uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe abanto yanto njengabo bangaphambili kunabo babengento yanto. Kananjalo Thina SithumeleiiVesi ezinobungqinaobucacileyo. Kwaye kwabangakholwayo sisohlwayo sehlazo
  58,6,"NgeMini uAllâh Aya kubavusa bonke, Abaxelele abakwenzayo. UAllâh Ukubalile, lo gama bakulibeleyo bona; kwaye uAllâh liNgqina ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  58,7,"Akuboni na ukuba uAllâh Wazi okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni? Akukho ncoko yabathathu (eyenzelwa ekhusini) koko Yena Uba ngowesine kubo, kungekho bahlanu koko Yena ngowesithandathu kubo akukho banganeno kunoko kungekho bangaphezulu kunoko koko Yena Ukunye nabo (ngolwazi) nokuba baphi na apho bakhoyo. Ke kaloku Uya kubaxelela ngoko bakwenzayo ngoMhla woVuko, Inene uAllâh, nguMazi weento zonke"
  58,8,"Akubabonanga na abo babalelwe (ukuba babe yinxalenye) yencoko yasekhusini? Babuyela ke koko babalelwe kuko bancokola phakathi kwabo ngesono nangogabadelo nokungabi nantobeko kuMthunywa (ka-Allâh). Ke kaloku xa befika kuwe bakubulisa ngombuliso Angakubulisi ngawo uAllâh, bathi: “ Kutheni na kaloku uAllâh Angasohlwayi ngoko sikutshiloyo?” Okwaneleyo kubo sisiHogo; abaya kungena kuso batshe, ayisembi ngako indawo yokugqibela yabo"
  58,9,"Hini na nina bakholwayo xa nincokola ekhusini musani ukuncokola ngesono, ugabadelo nangokungamthobeli uMthunywa koko ncokolani ngobulungisa nobunyulu. Noyike uAllâh Eniza kuqokelelwa (phambi) kwaKhe"
  58,10,"Iincoko zasekhusini zivela kuShaytân esenzela ukukhubekisa abo bakholwayo, kodwa akayi kubonzakalisa ngaphandle kokuba anikwe imvume nguAllâh. Ke kaloku amakholwa makaxhomekeke kuAllâh"
  58,11,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, xa nixelelwa ukuba: “Vulani izithuba phakathi kwenu,” entlanganisweni, vulani izithuba kaloku, uAllâh Uya kunenzela isithuba. Naxa niyalelwe ukuba: “Phakamani,” phakamani; uAllâh Uya kuba phakamisa abo bakholwayo phakathi kwenu nabo babenikwe ulwazi, ngokwamabakala kananjalo uAllâh Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo"
  58,12,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, xa nifuna ukuthetha noMthunywa bucala, nikelani ngamalizo phambi kokuthetha naye oko kukona kulungileyo kuni kwaye kububunyulu. Kodwa ke ukuba aninanto (yakunikela) inene uAllâh nguMxoleli nguSozinceba"
  58,13,"Ingaba niye noyika na ukuza nomnikelo phambi kokuthetha (naye)? Ke kaloku ukuba akunjalo uAllâh Unixolele yenzani iSalâh, ninikele ngeZakâh, nithobele uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe. Kananjalo uAllâh Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo"
  58,14,"Ubabonile na abo benza ubumbano nabantu uAllâh Anomsindo (ngakubo), bona abangobenu bengengabo nababo kwaye bafunga ubuxoki lo gama besazi (ukuba baya xoka)"
  58,15,UAllâh Ubalungiselele isohlwayo esibuhlungu kanobom. Inene kungcolile oko bakwenzayo
  58,16,"Bathabathe izifungo zabo zobuxoki bazenza into yokusithela baze baphambukisa (abantu) eNdleleni ka-Allâh, ke kaloku okwabo sisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  58,17,"Ubutyebi babo nabantwana babo asokuze bubancede nto ngokuchasene noAllâh. Abo ngamadlelane oMlilo, baya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade"
  58,18,"NgeMini uAllâh Aya kubavusa bonke, yaye baya kufunga kuYe njengoko befunga kuni becinga ukuba bemi phezu kwento kanti ngabo abangamaxoki"
  58,19,"UShaytân ubagqumile wabenza balibala ngokukhumbula uAllâh. Elo ke libandla likaShaytân, Inene, ibandla likaShaytân, lilo eliya kuba ngabalahlekelwa"
  58,20,Inene abo baphikisa uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe baya kuba phakathi kwabona bahlazeke ngokwenene
  58,21,"UAllâh Ubhalile Wathi: “ NdiM nabaThunywa baM Abaza kuphumelela.” Inene nguAllâh Onamandla nobungangamsha"
  58,22,"Awungekhe ubafumaneabantuabakholwakuAllâhnakwiMini yokugqibela bebathanda abo baphikisa uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, enokuba abo bantu ngooyise babo okanye ngoonyana babo, okanye ngabantakwabo okanye zizizalwana zabo na. Kwabo banjalo (uAllâh) Ubhale ukholo ezintliziyweni zabo, Wabaxhasa ngomoya ovela kuYe. Kananjalo (uAllah) Uya kubangenisa eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, bahlale apho (ngonaphakade). UAllâh Uya kukholiseka ngabo nabo bakholiseke nguYe. Bona balibandla lika-Allâh, Inene ibandla lika-Allâh, lilo eliza kuphumelela"
  59,1,"(Konke) okusemazulwini nokusemhlabeni kuzukisa uAllâh, yaye Yena nguSobunganga, nguSobulumko"
  59,2,"NguYe kanye Owagxotha abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi (amaYuda namaKhristu) emakhayeni abo kwindibano yokuqala1 Nina naningayicingi nokuyicinga into yokuba bangahamba, kanti nabo babecinga ukuba iinqaba zemikhosi yabo ziza kubakhusela kuAllâh; Kodwa ummiselo ka-Allâh wabafikela uvela apho babengawulindelanga khona, Wafaka ixhala ezintliziyweni zabo baza batshabalalisa izindlu zabo ngezandla zabo nangezandla zamakholwa. Ngoko ke thabathani isilumkiso nina bantu bakwaziyo ukubona"
  59,3,"Ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yokuba UAllâh Wayesele Emisele kukhutshwa kwabo, ngeWabohlwayayo kweli hlabathi ukanti okwabo kuBomi oBuzayo sisohlwayo soMlilo"
  59,4,Oko kungenxa yokuba baphikisa uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe. Ke kaloku lowo uphikisa uAllâh Inene uAllâh Wohlwaya kabuhlungu
  59,5,"Konke enikugawuleyo okuyimithi yabo yesundu neniyishiye imile ngeziqu zayo, (oko) kube ngemvume ka-Allâh kwaye Usaya kubahlaza abadelelayo, abangenantobeko"
  59,6,"Nantoni na uAllâh Ayibuyisele kuMthunywa waKhe evela kubo akukho mahashe (kungekho) zinkamela naziphalisela yona. Kodwa uAllâh Unika uMthunywa waKhe amandla ngaphezulu kwalowo athande (ukumnika amandla ngaphezu kwakhe), Yaye uAllâh Unamandla ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  59,7,"Ke kaloku nantoni na uAllâhAyibuyisela kuMthunywa waKhe ivela kubantu bezixeko yeka-Allâh noMthunywa waKhe nezizalwana zaKhe ezizezona zisondeleyo kuye neenkedama nababandezelekileyo nabaseluhambeni khona ukuze ingabi (yonto) iyakwabiwa umphelo phakathi kwabazizityebi naphakathi kwenu. Nantoni na uMthunywa aninika yona yithatheni nantoni na ke analele yona, shenxani kuyo. Noyike uAllâh kananjalo; inene uAllâh Wohlwaya kabuhlungu"
  59,8,"Kumahlwempu angabafuduki abagxothwa emakhayeni abo nakwimpahla yabo, befuna uBubele buka-Allâh nokwamkeleka kuYe, bexhasa uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, (banesabo isabelo nabo). Ngabanyanisekileyo ke abo"
  59,9,"(Banesabelo) Nabo babezinzile kumakhaya abo (eMadinah) baza balwamkela ukholo (lweIslam) ngaphambi (kokufika) kwabo (abafuduki), bona bayabathanda abo bafudukela kubo, yaye abanamona ezifubeni zabo ngoko bakunikiweyo (kuphuma kwixhayelo) kananjalo bona bakhetha ukuba kuqalwe (ngabafuduki) kunabo (bona bemi baseMadinah) nangona belifuna (ixhayelo). Nabani na lowo usindisiweyo ekunyolukeni kwakhe, abanjalo ngabo abaya kuphumelela"
  59,10,"Ke kaloku abo bafika emva kwabo bathi: “Nkosi yethu! Sixolele thina nabazalwana bethu abasandulelayo elukholweni, ungafaki nzondo ezintliziyweni zethu ngokuchasene nabo bakholiweyo. Nkosi yethu inene Wena unguSobubele, uSozinceba"
  59,11,"Akubabonanga na abahanahanisi, abathi koogxa babo abangabanye baBantu beNcwadi abangakholwayo: “Sifunga ngoAllâh ukuba nigxothiwe nina, nathi oku kwethu siya kuhamba nani, kwaye ukuba niyahlaselwa, inene siya kunincedisa thina.” Kodwa uAllâh liNgqina Yena lokuba bona ngamaxoki okwenene"
  59,12,"Inene, ukuba wona (amaYuda) agxothiwe, asokuze bona (abahanahanisi) bahambe nawo, kanti ke nokuba bangawancedisa (amaYuda lawo), (abahanahanisi) baza kuphinda beze ngomva (babaleke) yaye abayi kuba noloyiso"
  59,13,"Inene, nina (bakholwayo) noyikeka kakhulu ezintliziyweni zawo (amaYuda) kunoAllah, oko kungenxa yokuba bangabantu abangenangqiqo"
  59,14,Abasokuze balwe nani ngaphandle kokuba kungaphakathi kwezixeko ezikhuselekileyo okanye ngaphaya kweendonga. Ukruthakruthano phakathi kwabo luninzi. Nina nicinga ukuba bamanyene kodwa iintliziyo zabo zahlukene. Oko kunjalo ngenxa yukuba bangabantu abangaqiqiyo
  59,15,"Imfano yabo inje ngabo babengaphambi kwabo kwithuba elisandula kugqitha: bona ke bangcamla iziphumo zezenzo zabo, yaye basaza kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  59,16,"(Abahanahanisi) banjengoShaytân xa esithi emntwini, “Mus’ukukholwa.” Aze athi (umntu lowo) esakungakholwa, (uShaytân athi): “Inene, mna ndiyazikhwebula kuwe. Inene mna ndoyika uAllâh, iNkosi yamaphakade.”"
  59,17,"Ngoko ke isiphetho ngabo kukuba bekunye (noShaytân lowo wabo) baya kuba seMlilweni, bahlale apho ngonaphakade. Leyo ke yimbuyekezo yabenzi bobugwenxa"
  59,18,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, yoyikani uAllâh. Kananjalo umphefumlo ngamnye mawujonge okwenzileyo ukulungiselela ingomso. Inene uAllâh Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo"
  59,19,"Ningabi njengabo baMlibalayo uAllâh, Waza naye Wabenza oku kwabo bazilibala iziqu zabo. Abo ngabadelelayo, abangenantobeko"
  59,20,Akafani amadlelane oMlilo namadlelane ePaladesi. Amadlelane ePaladesi ngabazuzi bempumelelo
  59,21,"Ukuba le ‘Kur’ân Sasiyithumele entabeni, wawuya kuyibona izithoba idilika ngenxa yokoyika uAllâh. Le mizekeliso Siyinika abantu khon’ukuze bacingisise"
  59,22,"Yena nguAllâh, ekungekho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, uMazi wokungabonakaliyo nokubonakalayo. Yena nguSozinceba"
  59,23,"Yena nguAllâh ekungekho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe uKumkani, uSobungcwele, Ongenakusoleka, uMniki wokhuseleko, uMlondolozi wezidalwa zaKhe, uSobunganga, uMyaleli, Omkhulu, uzuko malube kuAllâh, Yena Ungentla lee koko bakwayamanisa naYe"
  59,24,"Yena nguAllâh, uMdali, uMyili, uMbumbi; ngawaKhe onke amagama amnandi. Konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni kuzukisa Yena. Kananjalo Yena nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  60,1,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, musani ukuthabatha iintshaba zaM neentshaba zenu (nizenze) abahlobo benu, lo gama zingakholwanga koko kwafika kuni (i’Kur’ân) kuyinyaniso, ekubeni babegxothe uMprofeti nani ngenxa yokuba nakholwayo kuAllâh, iNkosi yenu. Xa niphumele iJihâd (ukulwa) eNdleleni yaM nifuna indlela yokwamkeleka kuM, (musani ukubathabatha njengabahlobo benu). Nina nibabonisa uthando (emfihlakalweni) ukanti Mna Ndikwazi kakuhle enibonisana ngako nabo emfihlakalweni noko nibaxelela kona. Ke kaloku owenza oko phakathi kwenu ulahleke ngokwenene eNdleleni elungileyo"
  60,2,"Ukuba bangafumana ulongamelo phezu kwenu, bona baya kuba ziintshaba kuni, bolule izandla namalwimi abo angcolileyo ngokuchasene nani, yaye baninqwenelela ukuba ningakholwa"
  60,3,Asokuze izizalwana zenu okanye abantwana benu banincede nto; ngeMini yoVuko. Yena (uAllâh) Uya kugweba phakathi kwenu. Kananjalo uAllâh Uyakubona enikwenzayo
  60,4,"Ke kaloku Sele niwufumene owona mzekelo mhle kuIbrâhîm nabo babekunye naye, xa bathi kubantu bakubo, “Inene thina siyazahlulakuninakuloontoniyinqulayongaphandlekoAllâh. Siyaniphika, kananjalo sele kuvele ubutshaba nenzondwano phakathi kwethu nani ngonaphakade de nikholwe kuAllâh Yedwa,” ngaphandle nje kokuba uIbrâhîm waye wathi kuyise “Mna ndiya kukucelela itarhu inene, kodwa (andinagunya) lokukwenzela nantoni na ngokuchasene noAllâh: Nkosi yethu kukuWe apho sixhomekekileyo, kukuWe nalapho sibuyela khona kananjalo Wena Usisiphelo sohambo (lwethu)"
  60,5,"Nkosi yethu! senze singabi yonto yokungcungcuthekiswa ngabangakholwayo, Usixolele Wena, Nkosi yethu. Inene nguWe uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  60,6,Ke kaloku Inene nina kubo (ooIbrahim) nibe nowona mzekelo mhle kuye nabani na othemba lakhe linguAllâh neMini yokugqibela. Ke kaloku nabani na ofulathelayo inene uAllâh Akadingi nto ngoWokudunyiswa
  60,7,"Mhlawumbi uAllâh Uya kufaka phakathi kwenu nabo beniziintshaba kubo; uthando. Ke kaloku uAllâh Unamandla yaye uAllâh nguMxoleli, Unenceba"
  60,8,"UAllâh Akanaleli kwabo banganilwiyo ngenxa yenkolo (yenu)\tbenganigxothi\tnakumawenu\tukuba\tnibaphathe kakuhle nenze ubulungisa kubo. Inene uAllâh Uyabathanda abo benza ubulungisa"
  60,9,"UAllâh Unalele kuphela kwabo banilwayo ngenxa yenkolo (yenu) banigxothe nokunigxotha kumakhaya enu bancedisane nokugxothwa kwenu, (Akanivumeli ke) ukuba nenze ubuhlobo nabo, nabani na ke owenza ubuhlobo nabo abo (benza loo nto) ngabo kanye abangabenzi bobubi"
  60,10,"Hini na nina bakholwayo! Xa abafazi abakholwayo befika kuni bengabafuduki, baphenyeni (bacikideni). UAllâh nguYe Owaziyo ngokubhekiselele kukholo lwabo. Ke kaloku ukuba ngaba nibazi bengamakholwakazi, musani ukubabuyisela kwabangakholwayo, bona abangobafazi abavumelekileyo ngokusemthethweni kubo kanti nabo abangobayeni abavumelekileyo ngokusemthethweni kubo. Kodwa ke nikani abangakholwayo ababekuhlawulile (ngokubatshata). Ke kaloku akukho sono kuni ukuba niyabatshata xa nibanikileyo (abo bayeni babo babashiyileyo) imbuyekezo yabo efanekileyo. Kananjalo ningagcini maqhina omtshato nabafazi abangakholwayo koko bizani oko benikuhlawulile (ngabo). Nibavumele nabo babize oko babebekuhlawulile (ngani)1 Olo lugwebo luka Allâh; Uya gweba Yena phakathi kwenu, ke kaloku uAllâh, Uyazi, Unobulumko"
  60,11,"Ke kaloku ukuba ngaba nawuphi na umfazi uthe wemka kuni waya (kwicala) labangakholwayo nize nina nibize imbuyekezo yoko nakuhlawulayo ngabo, (kodwa bala bona), naza naphuma naya edabini (leGrazwa ngokuchasene nabo bangakholwayo) naza nafumana ixhayelo, hlawulani ngenxalenye yelo xhayelo okulingana noko kumele ukuhlawulwa loo madoda ashiywe ngabafazi bawo noyike uAllâh loWo nikholwa kuYe"
  60,12,"Hini na wena Mprofeti, xa abafazi abakholwayo befika kuwe (beze kwenza isibhambathiso), bevuma kuWe okokuba abasayi kwayamanisa nto kuAllâh, abayi kuba, abayi kukrexeza bengasayi kubabulala abantwana babo (ukuqhomfa), bengasayi kuthetha ubuqhetseba ngabom besenza ubuxoki (ngokuthi abantwana ababazeliswe ngamadoda wambi batyhole abayeni babo ngabo bantwana). Bengasayi kungakuthobeli wena ngoko kulungileyo. Samkele ke isibhambathiso sabo ubacelele itarhu kuAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguMxoleli, uSozinceba"
  60,13,Hini na nina bakholwayo musani ukwakha ubumbano nabantu uAllâh Anomsindo ngakubo. Bona balilahla (kudala) ithemba (lomvuzo) kuBomi oBuzayo njengabangakholwayo balilahlayo ithemba lokudibana nabo bangabemi basemangcwabeni
  61,1,"(Konke) okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni kuzukisa uAllâh kananjalo Yena nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  61,2,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, kungani na ukuba nithethe into ningayenziyo"
  61,3,Ichaseke kakhulu phambi koAllâh into yokuba nithethe into eningayenziyo
  61,4,Ke kaloku uAllâh Uyabathanda abo balwa eNdleleni yaKhe (bemi) belihlelo (umgca) babengathi basisiqu esinye esidityaniswe ngokuqinileyo
  61,5,"Yabona uMûsâ wathi kubantu bakubo: “Hini na bantu bakuthi, nindikhubekiselani na nisazi ngokuqinisekileyo nje okokuba mna ndinguMthunywa ka-Allâh kuni?” Ke kaloku bathi besakuphambuka, uAllâh Wenza iintliziyo zabo zaphambuka. Ke kaloku uAllâh Akabakhokeli abadelelayo, abangenantobeko"
  61,6,"Yabona xa u’Isâ, unyana ka Maryam, wathi: “Hini na Bantwana bakwaSirayeli, inene mna ndinguMthunywa ka- Allâh kuni, ndingqina oko kwafika ngaphambili kunam kukwiTorah, ndiniphathele iindaba ezivuyisayo zoMthunywa oza kufika emveni kwam, ogama lakhe linguAhmad.” Kodwa wathi esakufika kubo, bathi bona: “Lo ngumlingo ocacileyo.”"
  61,7,Ngubaninaintswelabulungisaegqithaoqambaokungeyonyani ngoAllâh lo gama emenyelwa kwi-Islam. Ke kaloku uAllâh Akabakhokeli abantu abangabenzi bobugwenxa
  61,8,"Banqwenela ukucima ukukhanya kuka-Allah, Uza kukufezekisa ukukhanya kwaKhe Yena, enokuba abangakholwayo bakuchase kangakanani na oko"
  61,9,"NguYe Othumele uMthunywa waKhe nesiKhokelo nenkolo yenyaniso ukuba ayibonakalise ngaphezulu kweenkolo zonke, enokuba abo bangabanquli zithixo bakuchase kangakanani na oko"
  61,10,Hini na nina bakholwayo ndinganikhokeleli kunaniselwano oluya kunisindisa esohlwayweni esibuhlungu
  61,11,"Kholwani kuAllâh noMthunywa waKhe nizabalaze eNdleleni ka-Allâh ngobutyebi benu nangobomi benu. Oko kokona kulungileyo kuni, ukuba benisazi"
  61,12,"Yena Uya kunixolela izono zenu, Aningenise eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo phantsi kwayo nemizi emihle eMiyezweni yokuhlala ngonaphakade. Leyo ke yimpumelelo enkulu"
  61,13,"Kananjalo niya kuzuza olunye uBabalo kuAllâh eniya kuluthanda noloyiso, vakalisa (Muhammad) iindaba ezivuyisayo kumakholwa"
  61,14,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, yibani ngabancedisi baka-Allah, njengangoko u’Isâ, unyana kaMaryam wathi kubafundi bakhe: “Ngoobani na abancedisi bam kuAllâh?” Abafundi bathi: “Thina singabo abancedisi baka-Allah.” Ke kaloku iqela (elithile) kuBantwana bakwaSirayeli laya alakholwa. Thina ke Sancedisa abo bakholwayo ngokuchasene neentshaba zabo, baza baba nolongamelo"
  62,1,"(Konke) Okusemazulwini nokusemhlabeni kuzukisa uAllâh, uKumkani, uSobungcwele, uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  62,2,"NguYe Othumele uMthunywa phakathi kwabangakwazi kubhala nakufunda, ephuma phakathi kwabo, ebacengcelezela iiVesi zaKhe, ebahlambulula, ebafundisa iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) nobulumko nangona ngaphambili babesekulahlekeni okucacileyo"
  62,3,"Kanti nakwabanye babo abangekadibani nabo. Yaye Yena nguSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  62,4,Obo bubuBele buka-Allâh Abunika lowo Athande ukumnika kwaye uAllâh nguMnini buBele obuninzi
  62,5,Umzekelo wabo babenikwe iTorah baza abayithabathela (ngqalelo) unjengalowo wembongolo ethwala imfumba yeencwadi (Kodwa kube kungekho nto iyiqondayo ngokubhalwe phakathi kwazo). Mmbi kanobom umzekelo wabantu abaphika iiVesi zika-Allâh. Ke Yena UAllâh Akabakhokeli abantu abenza ubugwenxa
  62,6,"Yithi: “Hini na nina maYuda! Ukuba ngaba nina nibanga ukuba ngabahlobo baka-Allah, (abanye) abantu abangabo, langazelelani ukufa kaloku ukuba nithetha inyaniso"
  62,7,Kodwa (nakanye) abangekhe bakulangazelele ngenxa yoko (kungcolileyo) kwenziwe zizandla zabo! Kananjalo uAllâh Uyabazi abenzi bobubi
  62,8,"Yithi: “Inene ukufa oko nikubalekayo kuza kugagana nani, Niya kubuyiselwa (kuAllâh), uMazi wokungabonwayo, kwaye Uza kunixelela ngoko nanikwenza"
  62,9,"Hini na nina bakholwayo xa umemezelo mthandazweni lukhwazwa ngemini yeJum’ah (uLwesihlanu) Yiyani kwinkumbulo ka-Allâh nishiye unaniselwano, (amashishini). Oko kokona kulungileyo kuni ukuba benisazi"
  62,10,"Ke kaloku wakuphetwa umthandazo, yithani saa elizweni nifune ubuBele buka-Allâh (ngokusebenza), nikhumbule uAllâh rhoqo kananjalo ukuze niphumelele"
  62,11,"Kodwa bona (abafundi bakho Muhmmad) bathi bakubona okuthengiswayo okanye okwabiwayo bangxamele kuko, bakushiye umile (apho wedwa). Yithi ke wena; “OkukuAllâh kuhle ngaphezulu kunentengiso, yaye uAllâh nguYena Ulungileyo kunabo bonke ababoneleli.”"
  63,1,"Xa abahanahanisi befika kuwe (Muhammad), bathi: “Siyangqina okokuba unguMthunywa ka-Allâh.” UAllâh Uyakwazi kakade okokuba unguMthunywa waKhe, uAllâh Yena Unika ubungqina bokuba abahanahanisi ngamaxoki"
  63,2,"Bathabatha izifungo zabo njengento yokusithela, baze baphambukise (abantu) eNdleleni ka-Allâh. Inene kungcolile oko bakwenzayo"
  63,3,Oko kungenxa yokuba baya bakholwa baphinda futhi bangakholwa; ngoko ke iintliziyo zabo zitywiniwe koko abaqondi bona
  63,4,"Ke kaloku xa ubajongile wena imizimba yabo iya kuxolisa naxa bethetha uphulaphule intetho yabo ibangathi zizijungqu zeenkuni ezimisiweyo. Bona bacinga ukuba lonke izwi elikhwazayo lichasene nabo. Balutshaba bona, balumkele ke wena. Wanga uAllâh Angabatshabalalisa, baqhatheke (baphuma) njani (eNdleleni)"
  63,5,"Naxa kusithiwa kubo: “Yizani uMthunywa ka-Allâh Uza kunicelela itarhu (kuAllâh),” banikina iintloko zabo ubabone nawe betshikila besimka ngenkukhumalo"
  63,6,"Kuyafana kubo nokuba ungabacelela itarhu okanye ungabaceleli, Akasokuze Abaxolele uAllâh, Inene uAllâh Akabakhokeli abantu abadelelayo abangenantobeko"
  63,7,"Bona ngabo bathi: “Musani ukunikela nto kwabo bakunye noMthunywa ka-Allâh de bachithakale (bamshiye).” Ke kaloku ngabaka-Allah oovimba bamazulu nomhlaba kodwa abahanahanisi abaqondi bona"
  63,8,"Bathi:“UkubasinokubuyelaeMadinah,oyenauhloniphekileyo uza kubagxotha abangento yanto phaya.” Kodwa intlonipheko, amandla nozuko zezika-Allah, noMthunywa waKhe namakholwa kodwa abazi abahanahanisi bona"
  63,9,"Hini na nina bakholwayo! Musani ukuvumela ubutyebi benu nabantwana benu baniphambukise eNdleleni ka-Allâh, nabani na owenza oko, abo ngabona bangabalahlekelwa"
  63,10,"Nikelani ke eNdleleni ka-Allâh koko Sininike kona phambi kokuba ukufa kufikele omnye wenu, aze athi: “Nkosi yam akwaba Ubunokukhe Undimele ixeshana elifutshane ukuze ndinikele kumalizo ndibe ngomnye wamalungisa.”"
  63,11,Kodwa (Yena) uAllâh Akasokuze Awumele umphefumlo xa sele lifikile ixesha lawo. Kananjalo uAllâh Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo
  64,1,"(Konke) okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni kuzukisa uAllâh, lolwaKhe ulongamelo kananjalo ukudunyiswa kokwaKhe, yaye Unamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  64,2,"NguYe\tOwanidalayo,\tukanti\tphakathi\tkwenu kukho abangakholwayo\tkwalapho\tphakathi\tkwenu\tkubekho abakholwayo. Kanti ke Yena uAllâh Uyakubona enikwenzayo"
  64,3,"Yena Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngenyaniso, Wanibumba Wazifezekisa izimo zenu kwaye kukuYe apho kuza kuphelelwa khona"
  64,4,"Uyakwazi okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni, Ekwazi kananjalo enikufihlayo nenikuchazayo, kwaye uAllâh nguMazi wokusezifubeni"
  64,5,"Azifikanga na iindaba zabo babengakholwa ngaphambili kunani? Bona bazingcamla iziphumo zomcimbi wabo, yaye baza kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  64,6,"Oko kungenxa yokuba abaThunywa babo babeye beze kubo benobungqina obucacileyo, kodwa bona bathi: “Singakhokelwa ngabantu thina kakade?” Baya abakholwa ke batshikila. Kodwa Yena uAllâh Wayengenamfuno yabo, uAllâh sisiTyebi, Ufanelwe zizo zonke iindumiso"
  64,7,"Abo bangakholwayo babanga ukuba abasokuze bavuswe. Yithi wena, “Ewe, ndifunga ngeNkosi yam, niya kuvuswa ngenene, kwaye niza kuxelelwa ngokwenene ngako (konke) enakwenzayo. Kulula oko kuAllâh. Sûrah 64 At-Tagrhâbun (ILahleko nenzuzo yamacal ‘omabini) ISahluko"
  64,8,Ke kaloku kholwani kuAllâh nakuMthunywa waKhe nasekukhanyeni (i’Kur’ân) eSinithumelele kona. Kananjalo uAllâh Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo
  64,9,"NgeMini Aya kunidibanisela iMini yendibano Leyo yiMini yembandezelo. Nabani na okholwayo kuAllâh, enze izenzo ezilungileyo Yena (uAllâh) Uya kumsusela izenzo ezigwenxa kuye, Amngenise naseMiyezweni ekumpompoza kuyo imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, apho baya kuhlala khona ngonaphakade. Leyo yiyona mpumelelo inkulu"
  64,10,"Ke bona abo bangakholwayo baphika iiVesi zeThu abo ngamadlelane oMlilo, baya kuhlala apho kuwo ngonaphakade, hayi ububi besiphelo sabo"
  64,11,"Akukho ntlekele ihlayo ingehli ngemvume ka-Allâh. Nabani na ke okholwayo kuAllâh uya kumkhokelela intliziyo yakhe, ke kaloku uAllâh ngumazi weento zonke"
  64,12,Thobelani uAllâh nithobele noMthunywa; kodwa ukuba niye nabuya umva ke (uxanduva) olusemagxeni oMthunywa weThu kukuvakalisa (umyalezo) ngokucacileyo
  64,13,UAllâh akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe. Kananjalo kukuAllâh apho amakholwa makabeke ithemba lowo khona
  64,14,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, inene phakathi kwabafazi benu nabantwana benu kukho abazintshaba kuni, ngoko ke balumkeleni kodwa ke ukuba niyabaxolela ninge aniboni, inene uAllâh nguMxoleli, uSozinceba"
  64,15,Ubutyebi nabantwana benu buluvavanyo (kuni) ukanti uAllâh Yena Unomvuzo omkhulu
  64,16,"Yoyikani uAllâh ke kangangoko ninako, niphulaphule nithobele, ninikele (eNdleleni ka-Allâh); kuya kulunga emiphefumlweni yenu (oko). Kananjalo lowo ukhuselekileyo ebugqolweni bomphefumlo wakhe, Abanjalo ngabo abaya kuphumelela"
  64,17,"Ukuba niboleke uAllâh, imboleko entle, Yena Uya (kuyibuyisa) ngokuphindeneyo kuni, Anixolele futhi. Ke kaloku uAllâh ngoYena Unombulelo noYena Unyamezelayo"
  64,18,"UMazi wokungabonwayo, nokubonwayo, uSobunganga, uSobulumko"
  65,1,"Hini na Mprofeti, xa nina (maMuslim) niqhawula umtshato nabafazi, wuqhawuleni (isiqalo) sexesha labo lokulinda nilibale kananjalo ixesha (labo) lokulinda, noyike uAllâh iNkosi yenu. Musani ukubagxotha kwimizi (yabayeni) babo nabo oku kwabo abafanelanga kuzimkela (phakathi exesheni apho) ngaphandle kokuba benze uburheletya ngokucacileyo. Leyo ke yimiqathango ka-Allâh. Nabani na ke ogabadela imiqathango ka-Allâh; uzonile (lowo) ngokwakhe buqu. Nina anazi nto; mhlawumbi uAllâh Angavelisa into engumahluko emva koko"
  65,2,"Xa ke sele (bephantsele) ukuzalisekisa ixesha elo nisengabagcina ngemvisiswano entle kungenjalo nahlukane nabo ngesihle. Nize namangqina amabini angamadoda angamalungisa phakathi kwenu, nimisele ubungqina obamkelekileyo kuAllâh. Oko kuyalelwa lowo ukholwayo kuAllâh nakwiMini yokuGqibela. Ke kaloku lowo umoyikayo uAllâh, Uya kumenzela indlela"
  65,3,Kananjalo Uya kumbonelela apho ebengalindelanga khona. Nabani na oxhomekeke kuAllâh Yena Wanele kuye. Inene uAllâh Uza kuyifezekisa eyaKhe injongo. UAllâh sele kakade Emmisele (lowo) ngeento zonke
  65,4,"Ke kaloku kwabo bangasalindelekanga ukuya exesheni phakathi kwabafazi benu ukuba niyathandabuza, elabo ixesha ziinyanga ezintathu, kanti nakwabo bangekayi exesheni. Bona abo bamithiyo ixesha labo (lokulinda emva koqhawulo mtshato) kukuba bade bazale nabani na ke omoyikayo uAllâh, Uya kumenzela lula umcimbi wakhe"
  65,5,"Lowo ngumyalelo ka-Allâh, Awuthumele phantsi kuni; nabani na lowo woyika uAllâh Uya kumsusela izenzo zakhe ezigwenxa kuye Amenzele mkhulu umvuzo wakhe"
  65,6,"Bahlaliseni apho nihlala khona ngendlela eninako (ukwenza ngayo) ningabenzibubingendlelayokubacinezela(nibaphathe kakubi). Ukuba ngaba bamithi ke, bahoyeni bade bazale. Ukuba banincancisela (iintsana zenu) banikeni intlawulo yabo ebafaneleyo kananjalo ngamnye kuni makalamkele icebiso lomnye ngendlela enesihle. Ke kaloku ukuba nenzelana ubunzima, abanye abafazi basenokumncancisela usana (uyise wosana)"
  65,7,"Ke kaloku indoda esisityebi mayithabathe kubutyebi bayo, leyo ingqwebo yayo incitshiweyo mayithabathe koko uAllâh Ayinike kona (yondle umfazi). UAllâh Akawuthwalisi umphefumlo umthwalo ngaphandle kwalowo Awunike wona, uAllâh Uya kuzisa emveni kobunzima, ubulula (ukuphumla)"
  65,8,Zingaphi izixeko ezaba nendelelo mayela nomyalelo weNkosi yazo nabaThunywa baYo. Sazithabatha ke ukuba zihlawule ityala Sazohlwaya ngesohlwayo esibi
  65,9,(Ngasinye kuzo ezo zixeko) sangcamla iziphumo ezibi zemeko yaso. Kwaye isiphumo semeko yaso saba yilahleko
  65,10,"UAllâh Ubalungiselele isohlwayo esibuhlungu; yoyikani uAllâhkengoko, hininaninabantubanengqondobakholwayo, uAllâh Uthumele umyalezo kuni (i’Kur’ân)"
  65,11,"(Uthumele) uMthunywa (uMuhammad), enicengcelezela iiVesi ezicacileyo zika-Allâh hon’ukuze ngazo Akhuphe ebumnyameni abo bakholwayo benza izenzo ezilungileyo Yena Uya kubangenisa eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, bahlale apho ngonaphakade. UAllâh Uya kumlungiselela (uMuhammad nabakholwayo) imbonelelo (entle)"
  65,12,NguAllâh Odale amazulu asixhenxe nomhlaba ngokukwanjalo. Umyalelo (waKhe) uhla phakathi kwawo khon’ukuze nazi okokuba Unamandla ngaphezulu kunezinto zonke kwanokuba uAllâh Ugubungele zonke izinto ngolwazi
  66,1,"Hini na Mprofeti, kungani na ukuba uzalele wena oko uAllâh Akwenze kwavumeleka kuwe? Wena usuke ufune imvume yabafazi bakho? Kanti Yena uAllâh nguMxoleli, nguSozinceba"
  66,2,"UAllâh sele Eyalele kuni ukuphela kwezifungo zenu nina (maMuslim). Ke kaloku uAllâh nguMkhuseli wenu, Uyazi, nguSobulumko"
  66,3,"Yabona; uMprofeti wahlebela omnye wabafazi bakhe (uHafsah) waza yena (uHafsah) wayixelela omnye (u’A- ishah). UAllâh Wenza okokuba yazeke kuye (uMthunywa); (uMthunywa) yena wachaza inxalenye wayishiya inxalenye yayo, ukumxelela kwakhe (uHafsah) ngayo, wathi yena: “Ngubani okuxelele oku?” Wathi yena (uMthunywa): “USolwazi, uMazisi nguYe (uAllâh) Ondixeleleyo.”"
  66,4,"Ukuba nina nobabini (bafazindini boMprofeti) ningabuyela kuAllâh ngenguquko (kuya kunilungela oko), iintliziyo zenu zithambekele (ngasekuphikisaneni noMprofeti); ukuba niyancedisana ke ngokuchasene naye, inene uAllâh nguMkhuseli wakhe, noJibrîl nabangamalungisa kumakholwa neengelosi ngapha koko, ngabancedisi (bakhe)"
  66,5,"Mhlawumbi iNkosi yakhe ukuba unokuqhawula umtshato nani (nonke) Ingambekela abafazi abangcono kunani abazinikeleyo (kuAllâh), bekholwa ngokuzinikeleyo, abanentobeko abaguqukayo, abakhonzayo, nabazilayo (abanye) babekhe benda nabaziintombi"
  66,6,"Hini na nina bakholwayo, zikhuseleni nina neentsapho zenu eMlilweni osivuthusi sawo singabantu namatye ekubekwe iingelosi phezu kwawo ezingqwabalala, zona azikhe zingamthobeli uAllâh kuloo nto Aziyalele yona koko zenza ezikuyalelweyo"
  66,7,Hini na nina bangakholwayo musani ukuzithethelela ngayo le Mini niya kubuyekezwa kuphela ngoko nanikwenzile
  66,8,"Hini na nina bakholwayo guqukani kuAllah ngenguquko enyanisekileyo, mhlawumbiiNkosiyenu Iyakunicamagushela izenzo zenu ezigwenxa kuni, Inigenise eMiyezweni ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo. NgeMini apho uAllâh Angayi kumhlaza uMprofeti nabo bakholwayo kunye naye. Ukukhanya kwabo kuya kuba ngaphambili kubo, (neeNcwadi zezenzo zabo) ezandleni zabo zokunene kananjalo baya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu sigqibelelisele ukukhanya kwethu, Usixolele (izono zethu) Inene Wena Unolwazi lweento zonke"
  66,9,"Hini na Mprofeti, zabalaza ngokuchasene nabangakholwayo nabahanahanisi, ube ngqwabalala kananjalo kubo. Indawo yabo yokubalekela sisiHogo ayisembi indawo abaza kuphelela kuyo"
  66,10,"UAllâh Wazisa ngomzekelo kwabo bangakholwayo: Umfazi kaNûh nomfazi kaLût. Bobabini bona babephantsi kwezicaka zethu ezibini ezingamalungisa kodwa bazingcatsha ngoko ke bona (abaProfeti babo) azanga babancede nto kuAllâh kananjalo kwathiwa kubo: “Ngenani eMlilweni kunye nabo bangenayo.”"
  66,11,"Kananjalo uAllâh Wenza umzekelo kwabo bakholwayo: Umfazi kaFir’awn, xa wathi: “Nkosi yam, ndakhele umzi ecaleni kwaKho ePaladesi, Undisindise kuFir’awn nezenzo zakhe, Undisindise nakumsebenzi wakhe (obubugwenxa), Undisindise nakubantu abenza ububi.”"
  66,12,"(Nomzekelo)kaMaryamintombika’ImrânOwabulondolozayo ubunyulu bakhe, ngoko ke Savuthela (engubeni yakhe) ngengelosi yeThu, waza wakholwa kumazwi eNkosi yakhe neziBhalo zaYo, kwaye yena (uMaryam) wayengomnye wababezinikele, benentobeko"
  67,1,"Usikelelekile loWo eSandleni saKhe kukho uBukumkani, Onamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  67,2,"Yena loWo Wadala ukufa nokuphila ukuze Anivavanye (kucace ukuba) nguwuphi na kuni olungileyo ngezenzo. Yena nguSobunganga, uMxoleli"
  67,3,"Yena lowo Wadala amazulu asixhenxe alekeneyo. Akuboni kungangqinelani endalweni kaSozinceba. Ngoko ke guquka ujonge (esibhakabhakeni), likhona na ithanda olibonayo"
  67,4,Phinda ujonge kwakhona okwesibini. (Oko) kujonga (kwakho) kuya kubuyela kuwe kuthobekile kudiniwe
  67,5,"Inene Sihombise izulu elikufuphi ngezibane (iinkwenkwezi), Senza kananjalo ngazo oko kugityiselwa ngako amashayâtîn (ooSathana), yaye Sibalungiselele isohlwayo seDangatya"
  67,6,"Ke kaloku okwabo bangakholwayo eNkosini yabo sisohlwayo sesiHogo, hayi ukuba libi kwekhaya (labo) lokugqibela"
  67,7,"Xa bejulwa kuso, beva ukubizela kwaso (okoyikisayo) lo gama sibila nokubila"
  67,8,"Siphantsela ukugqabhuka ngumsindo, maxa onke iqela (elithile) liphoswa ngaphakathi kuso, abagcini baso bayababuza: “Akuzanga kufike Mlumkisi na kuni?”"
  67,9,"(Baphendula) bathi bona: “Ewe, uMlumkisi wayefikile kuthi kodwasamphikisathinasathi:“UAllâhakukhontoAyithumele phantsi, nina (baLumkisi) aninto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba sekulahlekeni okukhulu.”"
  67,10,"Kananjalo baya kuthi: “Akwaba sasiphulaphule okanye saqiqa, ngesingabangakho phakathi kwamadlelane eDangatya loMlilo"
  67,11,"Ke kaloku baya kusivuma isono sabo, ngoko ke kude lee ngabahlali baseDangatyeni loMlilo"
  67,12,"Inene abo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo Engabonwayo, okwabo iya kuba kukuxolelwa nomvuzo omkhulu"
  67,13,"Ke kaloku nokuba ningazifihla iintetho zenu zasekhusini okanye niziveze elubala, Yena nguMazi woko kusezifubeni (zabantu)"
  67,14,"Akamelanga kwazi na loWo Wadalayo? Kananjalo Yena nguSobubele, Onolwazi (lweento zonke)"
  67,15,NguYe Owenza umhlaba waba phantsi kolawulo lwenu ngoko ke hambani phakathi kwamathambeka wawo nidle kwimbonelelo yaKhe ukanti kukuYe apho uvuko lukhoyo
  67,16,"Ingaba niziva nikhuselekile na ukuba Yena loWo Usezulwini Akanakuwenza umhlaba uniginye, uthi kananjalo ngokukhawuleza ujikeleze (nani)?”"
  67,17,Okanye niziva nikhuselekile ekubeni loWo Usezulwini Akanakuthumela isiphango samatye ngokuchasene nani na? Niya kwazi ke okokuba saba (sibi) kanjani na isilumkiso saM
  67,18,Kananjalo sele baphika kakade abo bangaphambili kunabo saba njani ke isiyalo saM
  67,19,"Abaziboni\tna\tiintaka\t(eziphaphazela)\tphezu\tkwabo ngamaphiko avuliweyo (ngaxa limbi) evalekile? Akukho bani uzibambayo (ukuba zibe sesibhakabhakeni) ngaphandle koSozinceba. Inene Yena nguSokubona ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  67,20,Kanti ngubani na onokuba ngumkhosi wenu anincede ngaphandle koSozinceba? Abangakholwayo abakho ntweni ngaphandle kwenkohliso
  67,21,Ingubani khona onokunondla ukuba Ebenokusuka Ayibambe imbonelelo yaKhe (kuni)? Kodwa bona bathe gqolo ngokudelela nokuchasa (inkolo)
  67,22,Ingaba lowo uhamba erhubuluza ngobuso bakhe ukhokeleleke ngcono na kunalowo umi nkqo eNdleleni ethe Tye
  67,23,"Yithi: “NguYe Onivelisileyo, Waninika ukuva nokubona neentliziyo, kuncinane eninombulelo ngako.”"
  67,24,"Yithi: “NguYe Onenze naba baninzi ngokuphindeneyo emhlabeni, yaye kukuYe apho niza kuqokelelwa khona.”"
  67,25,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Sinini na esisi thembiso, ukuba (nina bakholwayo) nithetha inyaniso?”"
  67,26,"Yithi: “Ulwazi (loko) lukuAllâh, mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo.”"
  67,27,"Kodwa ukusibona kwabo sisondela, ubuso babo bangakholwayo, buya kunxunguphala kuze kuthiwe (kubo): “Oko ke koko nanikubiza"
  67,28,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Niyabona phofu ukuba uAllâh Anganditshabalalisa ndawonye nabo bakunye nam okanye Asenzele inceba, ngubani ongabakhusela bona abangakholwayo esohlwayeni esibuhlungu"
  67,29,"Yithi: “NguSolubabalo; thina sikholiwe kuYe, kananjalo kukuYe apho sixhomekeke khona. Kwaye niza kwazi okokuba ngubani na osekulahlekeni okucacileyo.”"
  67,30,"Yithi: “Niyijongile phofu (yona into yokuba): xa amanzi wenu ebenokusuka atshoniswe emhlabeni, ngubani omnye obeza kunizela namanzi ampompozayo"
  68,1,Nûn. (Ndifunga) ngosiba lokubhala nangoko (iingelosi) zikubhalayo
  68,2,"Wena\tngobabalo\tlweNkosi\tyakho\t(Muhammad) akuphambenanga"
  68,3,Inene okwakho ngumvuzo ongekhe usilele
  68,4,"Kananjalo\tinene\twena\t(ungumntu)\toziphethe\tkakuhle kakhulu"
  68,5,"Ngoko ke uza kubona, nabo baza kubona"
  68,6,Okokuba nguwuphi na kuni othwaxwa (nguSathana)
  68,7,"Inene iNkosi yakho yiYo Eyaziyo okokuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, IkwayiYo Ebaziyo abakhokelelekileyo"
  68,8,Ungawathobeli ke amaxoki
  68,9,"Wona anqwenela ukuba ugobele ngakuwo, kanti ngawo amakagobele (ngakuwe)"
  68,10,Kananjalo ungamthobeli nawuphi na umfungeli ongento yanto
  68,11,Umhlebi ohamba esasaza intlebendwane ngolunya
  68,12,"Umthinteli wokulungileyo, ogabadelayo, ongumoni"
  68,13,"Isikhohlakali, umgqakhwe1, ongumkhohlisi ngaphezulu"
  68,14,Ngenxa yokuba enobutyebi nabantwana
  68,15,"Xa iiVesi zeThu zicengcelezwa kuye, uthi: “Zintsomi zabantu bakudala!”"
  68,16,Siya kumtshisa enyhekeni yena
  68,17,Inene Sibalingile bona njengoko Salinga amahlulelane esitiya xa afungela ukuya kukha iziqhamo zaso ekuseni
  68,18,"Engatsho nokuthi: “(ukuba iNkosi Ivumile).”"
  68,19,Ke kaloku kwafika kuso apho (esitiyeni) isibetho esivela eNkosini yakho (satsha isitiya eso) esalele wona
  68,20,"Ekuseni Yaba ngathi sivuniwe (kwasa simnyama thsuh, sele sitshe salilahle)"
  68,21,Ke kaloku (ukuvuka kwawo amahlulelane lawo esitiya) abizana kwakusa
  68,22,"(Esithi omnye komnye): “Yiya kwakusekusasa ezityalweni zakho xa usiya kukha iziqhamo.”"
  68,23,Aphuma ke ethethela phantsi
  68,24,"(Esithi): “Akuyi kungena kuni nawuphi na umntu olihlwempu namhlanje"
  68,25,"Ahamba ke kusekwangoko ngokuzimisela, ezicingela ukuba anamandla (okuthintela wonke ubani okanye amahlwempu anokuthi athabathe iziqhamo zesitiya sawo)"
  68,26,"Kodwa athi esakusibona athi: “Inene thina siselahlekweni"
  68,27,Ngapha koko sibandezelekile!”
  68,28,"Oyena uthobekileyo kuwo wathi: “Andikhanga nditsho na kuwe ukuba zukisa (uAllâh)?”"
  68,29,"Bathi (omnye komnye): “Uzuko malube kwiNkosi yethu, inene thina sibe singabenzi bobubi.”"
  68,30,Ke kaloku (baqalisa) ukusondelelana begxekana
  68,31,"Bathi: “Yeha kuthi, inene thina sibe ngabagabadeli"
  68,32,"Mhlawumbi iNkosi yethu Iya kusinika into engcono kunaso, inene thina eNkosini yethu singabaneminqweno.”"
  68,33,"Saba njalo ke isohlwayo (seli hlabathi) nesohlwayo selizayo esingaphaya, ukuba bebesazi"
  68,34,"Inene\tokwabenzi\tbokulungileyo\tyiMiyezo\tyolonwabo eseNkosini yabo"
  68,35,Ingaba Siza kuphatha amaMuslim njengezaphula- mthetho na
  68,36,Kwenzeka ntoni na kuni? Kanti lunjani na ugwebo lwenu
  68,37,Okanye mhlawumbi ninesibhalo enifunda sona
  68,38,Eniza kufumana konke enikunqwenelayo (ngaso)
  68,39,"Okanye nineminqophiso (esisibophelelo) kuThi, eqhuba iye kuma kwiMini yoVuko, (ekubonakala) okokuba niya kuba noko nigwebe ukuba nibe kuko"
  68,40,Babuze okokuba nguwuphi na apha kubo oza kukumela ngenene oko
  68,41,Okanye mhlawumbi banamahlulelane? Mabeze namahlulelane abo kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  68,42,"NgeMini ubuqu buka-Allâh buya kutyhileka, ke kaloku baya kubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (kuAllâh) kodwa (abahanahanisi) abayi kukwazi ukukwenza oko"
  68,43,"Amehlo abo aya kuthotyelwa phantsi, bathiwe wambu kukuhlazeka; kaloku babedla ngokubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (emthandazweni) besenempilo entle (ehlabathini)"
  68,44,"Ndiyeke ke Mna (Muhammad Ndiqubisane) nalowo uyiphikayo le ntetho (i’Kur’ân), Thina Siya kumana ukubakhokelela apho bangaziyo"
  68,45,"Yaye Ndiya kubanika ixesha, inene elaM icebo liqinile"
  68,46,Makube mhlawumbi ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo Myalezo) ekucaca okokuba bazifumanisa benetyala elingumthwalo kubo
  68,47,"Okanye mhlawumbi banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  68,48,"Yiba nomonde ke wena ngesigqibo seNkosi yakho, ungabi njengomfo wentlanzi (uYûnus) xa wakhwazayo ekwimo yonxunguphalo"
  68,49,"Ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yenceba eyavela eNkosini yakhe eyamgubungelayo, ngewayejulwe elunxwemeni oluze enokusoleka"
  68,50,Ke kaloku iNkosi yakhe yamkhetha yamenza ilungisa
  68,51,"Inene abo bangakholwayo bebengakwenza utyibilike ngamehlo abo (ngendlela abakujonga ngayo) xa besiva umyalezo kananjalo bathi, “Inene yena ushiywe ziingqondo.”"
  68,52,Kodwa akunto yimbi oku ngaphandle kokuba sisikhumbuzi emazweni
  69,1,INyaniso
  69,2,Yintoni na iNyaniso
  69,3,Yintoni na enokukwazisa ukuba iyintoni na iNyaniso
  69,4,AmaThamûd nama’Ad ayiphika intlekele ebethayo (ukubetha kweYure yoMgwebo)
  69,5,Ke kaloku amaThamûd (lawo) atshatyalaliswa sisithonga esongamelayo
  69,6,"Nama’Ad\t(nawo)\tatshatyalaliswa\tngumoya\tovuthuza ngokutswinayo"
  69,7,"Lowo Yena uAllâh Wawunyanzelayo phezu kwabo ubusuku obusixhenxe neemini ezisibhozo zilandelelana, wawungababona abantu apho bedunduluzile bengathi ngamaphanga ezibhukubhuku zemithi yesundu"
  69,8,Ukhona ombonayo kubo (osaphilayo)
  69,9,Kwaza kweza uFir’awn nabo babengaphambili kunaye abazivuyavuyayo izixeko ngesono
  69,10,"Baya ababathobela abaProfeti beNkosi yabo, Yabahlasela ke ngohlaselo olumandla"
  69,11,"Inene athi amanzi akuphuphuma, Sanithwala nina (ookhokho benu) enqanaweni eyayidada (kaNûh)"
  69,12,Khon’ukuze Siyenze ibe sisikhumbuzi kwanokuba indlebe evayo iphaphame ngayo
  69,13,Xa iXilongo livuthelwa ngesithonga esinye
  69,14,Umhlaba neentaba ziphakanyisiwe zaphinda (zagangathwa) zeetyaba ngesithonga esinye
  69,15,Ngaloo Mini ke isehlo (uVuko) siya kuhla
  69,16,Nezulu liya kucandeka kubini (livuleke) kuba ngayo loo Mini liya kuba yacuyacu libe dlaka-dlaka
  69,17,"Ke kaloku emacaleni alo kuya kuba kukho iingelosi, ezisibhozo ngalooMini ziya kuba zithwele iTrone yeNkosi yakho phezu kwazo"
  69,18,"Ngayo loo Mini niya kuziswa ekugwetyweni, akukho mfihlo yenu iya kufihlakala"
  69,19,"Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sokunene uya kuthi: “Nantsi! Fundani iNcwadi yam"
  69,20,“Inene mna ndaye ndakholwa ukuba ndiza kudibana nokubhaliweyo (ngam)
  69,21,"Lowo ke uya kuba sebomini, obumnandi"
  69,22,Epaladesi ephakamileyo
  69,23,Iziqhamo zona ziya kuba ngezipho eziya kuba sezantsi kufutshane esandleni (sakhe)
  69,24,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yidlani nizanelise ngenxa yoko nazenzela kona (kwangethuba) ngemihla eyadlulayo.”"
  69,25,"Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sokhohlo, uya kuthi: “Yeha kum, akwaba bendingayinikwanga iNcwadi yam"
  69,26,Andayazi kwa ukuyazi into ebhalwe ngam
  69,27,Akwaba (ukufa kwam) bekusisiphelo sobomi bam
  69,28,Ubutyebi bam abundincedanga nto
  69,29,Igunya lam limkile kum (nokuhlonipheka kuphelile kum)!2”
  69,30,"(UAllâh Uya kuthi), “Mbambeni nimkhonkxe"
  69,31,Nimqhubele eDangatyeni loMlilo (wesiHogo)
  69,32,"Nimqamangele ngekhonkco\telibude balo\tbuzii kubite ezingamashumi asixhenxe"
  69,33,"Inene yena wayengakholwa kuAllâh, Ongoyena Mkhulu.”"
  69,34,Engazanga akhuthaze nokondliwa kwamahlwempu
  69,35,"Ngoko\tke\takasenaye namhlobo wakhe\tosenyongweni namhlanje"
  69,36,"Engenakutya\tkumbi\tngaphandle\tkwencindi\tephuma ezilondeni (ububomvu)"
  69,37,Akukho nabani na oya kuyitya (loo ncindi) ngaphandle kwaboni
  69,38,Ndifunga ngoko nikubonayo
  69,39,Nangoko ningakuboniyo
  69,40,"(Okokuba),\tinene\t(i’Kur’ân)\tililizwi\tlomthunywa ohloniphekileyo"
  69,41,"Kananjalo ayilolizwi lembongi, kuncinane enikukholelwayo"
  69,42,"Ingelolizwi lomvumisi, kuncinane enikukhumbulayo"
  69,43,(Yona) sisiTyhilelo esivela kwiNkosi yamaphakade
  69,44,Ukanti ukuba ngaba yena (uMuhammad) ebengaqamba iintetho zobuxoki ngaThi
  69,45,Ke kaloku beSiya kumxhakamfula ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  69,46,Size Simqhawule umthambo (wegazi osuka entliziyweni)
  69,47,Kwaye akukho namnye kuni obeya (kuSithintela Thina) kuye
  69,48,Inene yona (i’Kur’ân) isisikhumbuzi kumalungisa
  69,49,"Kananjalo, Siyazi Thina okokuba phakathi kwenu kukho abaphiki"
  69,50,Ke kaloku yona (i’Kur’ân) iya kuba ngunobangela wokuzisola kwabangakholwayo
  69,51,Yona ke ngenene iyinyaniso yokwenene
  69,52,(Wena) zukisa igama leNkosi yakho eNkulu
  70,1,Umbuzi wabuza ngesohlwayo esele siza kuhla
  70,2,Phezu kwabangakholwayo ekungekho bani unokusijika
  70,3,"Sivela kuAllâh, uMnini weendlela ezinyukayo"
  70,4,Iingelosi noMoya (oyiNgcwele) ziya kunyuka ziye kuYe ngeMini ebude bayo bungamawaka angamashumi amahlanu
  70,5,Linda ke ngomonde omhle
  70,6,Inene bona bayibona (ngathi) imgama
  70,7,Kodwa Thina Siyibona ikufuphi
  70,8,NgoMhla isibhakabhaka siya kuba njenge-oli emdaka
  70,9,Iintaba zibe njengoboya
  70,10,Akuyi kubakho mhlobo uya kubuza ngomhlobo (wakhe)
  70,11,Baya kubonana. Umoni uya kunqwenela ukuba akwaba ebeza kuhlawulelwa (akhululwe) esohlwayweni saloo Mini ngabantwana bakhe
  70,12,Nangomkakhe nomntakwabo
  70,13,Nezizalwana zakhe ezizezona zisondeleyo kuye ezamnika indawo yokuhlala
  70,14,Naye wonke osemhlabeni ukuba amsindise
  70,15,Nakanye! Inene iya kuba liDangatya (loMlilo wesiHogo)
  70,16,Oxwantsula (utshise) intlonze (yentloko)
  70,17,Ubize (bonke) abafulathela (inyaniso) balushiya ukholo
  70,18,Baqokelela ubutyebi babufumba
  70,19,Inene umntu wadalwa waxhalaba (wasisingxami)
  70,20,Xa ububi (intsokolo) bumchukumisa akanyamezeli
  70,21,Xa okulungileyo (ubutyebi) kumchukumisa abe nobugogotya (abe ligqolo)
  70,22,Ngaphandle kwabo bazinikeleyo kwiSalâh (emthandazweni)
  70,23,Abo benza iSalah yabo rhoqo
  70,24,"Nabo\tebutyebini\tbabo\tkukho\tamalungelo\tazekayo (kwabasweleyo)"
  70,25,"Kumngqibi ocelayo, nalowo ubandezekileyo, ulahlekelwe yimpahla nobutyebi bakhe"
  70,26,Nabo bakholwayo kwiMini yembuyekezo
  70,27,Nabo banoloyiko lwesohlwayo seNkosi yabo
  70,28,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yabo seso kungekho namnye ungaziva ekhuselekile kuso
  70,29,Nabo babulondolozayo ubunyulu babo
  70,30,"Ngaphandle kwakubafazi babo nabo babanjwe zizandla zabo zokunene, bona abanakusoleka"
  70,31,"Kodwa ke lowo ufuna okungaphaya kunoku, inene abenza njalo ngabagabadeli"
  70,32,Ke bona abo bagcina intembeko nezithembiso zabo
  70,33,Nabo baqinayo kubungqina babo
  70,34,Nabo bazilondolozayo kakuhle iiSalâh zabo
  70,35,Abo ngabo baya kuba seMiyezweni benentlonipheko
  70,36,"Yintoni kanye ngabo bangakholwayo, bengxama phambi kwakho nje (Muhammad)"
  70,37,"(Bahlale)\tekunene\t(kwakho)\tnasekhohlo\t(kwakho) bengamaqela ahlukeneyo"
  70,38,Ingaba ngamnye kubo ulangazelela ukungena eMyezweni wolonwabo
  70,39,Nakanye! Thina Sibadale ngoko bakwaziyo
  70,40,"Ngoko\tke\tNdifunga\tngeNkosi\tyeempuma\tneentshona okokuba Thina inene Sinamandla"
  70,41,Singabeka abanye abangcono endaweni yabo; yaye akukho nto inokuSithintela Thina
  70,42,Bayeke ke wena bancokole ubuvuvu bazonwabise bade bahlangane neMini yabo abathenjiswe ngayo
  70,43,NgeMini abaya kuphuma ngokungxama emangcwabeni bangxame ngathi baya esithixweni esimisweyo
  70,44,"Amehlo abo ethotyiselwe phantsi, ihlazo liya kuba libambethe. YiMini abathenjiswe ngayo ke leyo"
  71,1,"Inene, Thina Sathumela uNûh kubantu bakubo, (Sisithi): “Lumkisa abantu bakuni phambi kokuba bafikelwe sisohlwayo esibuhlungu.”"
  71,2,"Wathi yena: “Hini na bantu bakuthi! Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo kuni"
  71,3,"(Ndisithi kuni):‘KhonzaniuAllâh, noyikeYena, nindithobele.’"
  71,4,"Wathi, ‘(UAllâh) Uya kunixolela izono zenu Aze Animele (Ngesohlwayo) ixesha elikhethiweyo. Inene ixesha elikhethwe nguAllâh xa sele lifikile, aliyi kubanjezelwa, ukuba benisazi.’”"
  71,5,"Wathi: “Nkosi yam inene mna ndibamemile abantu bakuthi ubusuku nemini.”"
  71,6,Kodwa ukubamema kwam akubenzelanga nto ngaphandle (kokubongezelela) ukubaleka (enyanisweni)
  71,7,"Kananjalo maxa onke ndibamema (ndisithi kubo) Uya kuba xolela Wena, (Basuka) bafake iminwe yabo ezindlebeni zabo, bazigqume ngeengubo zabo bale bakhukhumale ngenkukhumalo (enkulu)"
  71,8,Ndibamemile esidlangalaleni
  71,9,"Ndaphinda ndenza isibhengezo, (ndathetha) nabo ekhusini"
  71,10,"Ndisithi (kubo): “Celani itarhu eNkosini yenu. Inene Yona, nguMxoleli wanaphakade"
  71,11,Yona Iya kunithumelela (imvula) esibhakabhakeni ingumkhumezelo
  71,12,"Iya kunandisela ubutyebi nabantwana, Ininike izitiya, nemilambo.”"
  71,13,"Yintoni na ngani le nto ningamoyikiyo uAllâh, ningenalo nethemba lomvuzo (ovela kuYe)"
  71,14,Lo gama Yena Wanidala ngokwamanqanaba ahlukeneyo
  71,15,"Aniboni na ukuba uAllâh Wawadala kanjani na amazulu asixhenxe, elinye phezu kwelinye"
  71,16,"Wenza inyanga yaba kukukhanya apho, ilanga lona laba sisibane"
  71,17,UAllâh Wanikhupha eluthulini lomhlaba
  71,18,Emva kwethuba Uza kunibuyisela kwakuwo (umhlaba lowo) Aphinde Anibuyise kwakhona (ngeMini yoVuko)
  71,19,Kananjalo uAllâh Unenzele umhlaba waphangalala
  71,20,Khona ukuze nihambe apho kuwo ezindleleni ezivulekileyo
  71,21,"UNûh wathi: “Nkosi yam baye abandithobela mna, balandela lowo ubutyebi bakhe nabantwana bakhe bungamongezeleli nto ngaphandle kwelahleko"
  71,22,Kananjalo bona baqulunqe iyelenqe elikhulu
  71,23,"Bathi: “Ningabashiyi oothixo benu; ningamshiyi uWadd, uSuwâ, uYagrhûth uYa-’û’k noNasr"
  71,24,Kananjalo balahlekise abaninzi. Ke kaloku (Wena Allâh) ‘Ungabandiseli nto abenzi bobubi ngaphandle kokulahleka”’
  71,25,Ngenxa yezono zabo baye batshoniswa emanzini baza bangeniswa eMlilweni. Abazanga bafumana mncedi wumbi endaweni ka-Allâh
  71,26,"Ke kaloku uNûh wathi: “Nkosi yam Ungashiyi namnye kwabangakholwayo phezu komhlaba"
  71,27,"Ukuba Ubashiyile, baya kulahlekisa izicaka zaKho yaye abayi kuzala nto ngaphandle kwezingcoli (ezinoburheletya), ezingakholwayo"
  71,28,Nkosi yam! Ndixolele mna nabazali bam nongena endlwini yamelikholwanamakholwanamakholwakazionke. Kekaloku kubenzi bobubi ungongezi nto ngaphandle kwentshabalalo.”
  72,1,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Kuye kwatyhilwa kum okokuba iqela leejinni1 liye laphulaphula (ucengcelezo lwe’Kur’ân), lathi; “Inene thina sive i’Kur’ân engummangaliso"
  72,2,"Ikhokelela eNdleleni elungileyo, kananjalo sikholiwe thina kuyo yaye asisayi kwayamanisa namnye eNkosini yethu"
  72,3,Kananjalo (yona ifundisa okokuba) Osenyangweni ngoYena UyiNkosi yethu Ehloniphekileyo; Yena Akathabathanga mfazi nanyana
  72,4,Ke kaloku osisidenge phakathi kwethu (uSathana) ebekade ethetha ugabadelo olubi ngoAllâh
  72,5,Ukanti thina besihleli sicinga okokuba abantu neejinni azimelanga kuthetha buxoki ngoAllâh
  72,6,"Kananjalo bekukade kukho ebantwini abo bafuna ukhuseleko kwiiJinni, zona ke zabongezelela ubudenge kuphela"
  72,7,Nazo bezicinga kanye njengoko benicinga zisithi uAllâh Akanakuze Athumele bani (ukuba abe nguMthunywa)
  72,8,Kananjalo thina sazama ukuya ezulwini kodwa sasuka salifumana lizeliswe ngabalindi abanamandla namadangatya avuthayo
  72,9,Ke kaloku thina sasidla ngokuncathama kwimimandla yezulu ukuya (kubisa) siphulaphule kodwa ophulaphulayo ngoku uya kufumana idangatya lomlilo limlalele
  72,10,"Kananjalo asazi nokuba kokungcolileyo na oko kuza kuhlela abo basemhlabeni, singazi nokuba iNkosi yabo Isingisele ekubabekeni eNdleleni elungileyo na"
  72,11,"Bakhona abangamalungisa phakathi kwethu, babe abanye bengenjalo, singamaqela aneendlela ezahlukeneyo"
  72,12,"Kananjalo sicinga ukuba asinako ukusiphepha isohlwayo sika-Allâh emhlabeni, singekhe siMphephe nangokubhabha"
  72,13,Ke kaloku thina ukusiva kwethu isikhokelo siye sakholwa kuso. Ke kaloku lowo ukholwa eNkosini yakhe akayi kuba naloyiko lwasinciphiso somvuzo wezenzo zakhe ezilungileyo okanye ukongezelelwa kwesohlwayo sezono zakhe
  72,14,"Kananjalo phakathi kwethu kukho abangamaMuslim kuze phakathi kwethu kubekho ama’kâsit (abangakholwayo), abo bamkele i-Islam, abanjalo bazifumanele iNdlela elungileyo.”"
  72,15,Ke wona ama’kâsit aya kuba ziinkuni zesiHogo
  72,16,"Ukuba ngaba bona (abangakholwayo) bebenokukholwa kuAllâh, bahambe eNdleleni elungileyo, beSiza kubapha indyebo yamanzi (imvula)"
  72,17,"Ukuze Sibalinge ngawo. Ngoko ke lowo ukreqayo kwinkumbulo yeNkosi yakhe [i’Kur’ân, (iNkosi yakhe)] Iya kumenza angene kwisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  72,18,"Kananjalo Yona (Ityhile) okokuba iimasjid zezika-Allah, ngoko ke musani ukunqula wumbi (kuzo)"
  72,19,"Ke kaloku ukuphakama kwesiCaka sika-Allâh (uMuhammad) sinqula iNkosi yaso emthandazweni, zona (iijinni) zenza isangqa ziyinyambalala zingathi enye ikhwele phezu kwenye (ukuza kuphulaphula)"
  72,20,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndinqula iNkosi yam (kuphela) yaye andayamanisi mahlulelane kuYo.”"
  72,21,"Yithi: “Akukho phantsi kwagunya lam ukuba nihlelwe bu bubi, okanye ukuningenisa eNdleleni elungileyo.”"
  72,22,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Akukho namnye ongandikhusela kwisohlwayo sika-Allâh, ndingeze ndifumane lukhuseleko ngaphandle kwakuYe"
  72,23,"Okwam kukuvakalisa okuvela kuAllâh nomyalezo waKhe. Nabani na lowo ungaMthobeliyo uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, inene okwakhe lowo nguMlilo wesiHogo, uya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade.”"
  72,24,"(Abayi kukholwa) de babone oko babethenjiswe ngako, baya kwazi ngoko ke ukuba ngubani na kanye ekungekho yakhe ngokubhekiselele kubancedisi, noyena ungento yanto mayela nenani (labancedisi)"
  72,25,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna andazi nokuba oko nithenjiswe ngako sele kukufuphi na nokuba iNkosi yam Iya kukubekela ixesha elide kusini na"
  72,26,Yena Yedwa (uAllâh) nguSolwazi wokungabonwayo kwaye Akakubonisi nabani na okungabonwayo kwaKhe.”
  72,27,"Ngaphandle kwalowo Athande (ukumbonisa) kubaThunywa baKhe, Inene Yena Uthumela phambi kwakhe (umthunywa lowo waKhe) nasemva kwakhe abakhi-mkhanyo"
  72,28,"(Yena uAllâh) Uyabakhusela (abaThunywa baKhe) Ade Abone okokuba bona (abaThunywa) bayivakalisile imiyalezo yeNkosi yabo (uAllâh), kwanokuba Yena Ugubungele konke oko kukunye nabo kwaye Yena (uAllâh) Ubala izinto zonke"
  73,1,Hini na wena uzisongele (ngeengubo)
  73,2,"Vuka (uthandaze) ebusuku, nokuba kukancinane"
  73,3,Isiqingatha sabo ubusuku okanye unciphise nokuba yintwana kuso
  73,4,"Okanye uyongeze, ucengceleze i’Kur’ân ngocengcelezo olulinganiselweyo"
  73,5,Inene Thina Siya kuphosa phezu kwakho ilizwi elinzima
  73,6,Inene iiyure zobusuku zizona zinemvakalo (entliziyweni naselwimini) yaye zilunge ngakumbi emazwini
  73,7,Inene okwakho ebudeni bemini kukuxakeka (okuthabatha ithuba) elide
  73,8,"Khumbula\tigama\tleNkosi\tyakho,\tuzinikele\tkuYo ngokuzinikela okupheleleyo"
  73,9,"(Yena uAllâh) YiNkosi yeMpuma neNtshona; akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, wena zithabathele Yena ukuba Abe nguMpumelelisi wemicimbi (yakho)"
  73,10,"Yiba nomonde nangoko bakutshoyo (ngawe), ungabahoyi kananjalo wena ngokungahoyi okuyindlela elungileyo"
  73,11,"Ubayekele kuM abaphiki, abo bahamba lula (ebomini), bamele okwethutyana"
  73,12,Inene kuThi kukho amakhamandela (okubabopha) noMlilo ovuthayo
  73,13,"Nokutya\tokukrwitshayo\t(okomayo).\tNesohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  73,14,NgeMini umhlaba neentaba ziya kungcangcazela zize iintaba zibe yinduli yentlabathi echithakala phantsi
  73,15,"Inene Thina Sithumele uMthunywa kuni (bantu), olingqina phezu kwenu njengoko Sasithumele uMthunywa kuFir’awn"
  73,16,"Kodwa yena uFir’awn akazanga amthobele uMthunywa, Samhlasela ke ngohlaselo olutshabalalisayo"
  73,17,"Ningayoyika njani ningakholwa nakukholwa kuyo, iMini leyo iya kwenza abantwana babe nezimvi"
  73,18,Izulu liya kuqhekeka lahlukane ngayo (loo Mini) kwaye esaKhe (uAllâh) isithembiso siyazaliseka
  73,19,"Inene le yinkumbuzo, lowo uthandayo makathabathe iNdlela eya eNkosini yakhe"
  73,20,"INkosi yakho Iyakwazi (Muhammad) ukuba uyaphakama (uthandaze) phantse izahlulo ezibini kwezithathu zobusuku okanye isiqingatha sabo, okanye isithathu sabo, Lenza njalo ke neqela labo bakunye nawe. Ke kaloku uAllâh Uyabazi (ubude) bobusuku nobemini. Uyazile Yena into yokokuba nina (maMuslim) aninakukwazi ukwenza njalo, Waza Wabuyela kuni ngenceba, ngoko ke cengcelezani okulula (kuni) kwe’Kur’ân. Uyazile nento yokuba kuza kuye kubekho abanye abagulayo phakathi kwenu, abanye babeseluhambeni emhlabeni befuna okuvela kwiziBele zika- Allâh, abanye (benu) besilwa eNdleleni ka-Allâh. Ngoko ke nina cengcelezani okulula kuyo, nenze iSalâh ninikele ngeZakâh, niboleke uAllâh imboleko entle. Ke kaloku nantoni na elungileyo eniza nayo ngaphambili ngokwenu, niya kuyifumana kuAllâh. Iya kuba ngcono ibe nkulu ngokomvuzo. Celani itarhu kuAllâh Inene uAllâh Uyaxolela, Unenceba"
  74,1,Hini na wena uzithe wambu ngeengubo
  74,2,Vuka ulumkise
  74,3,INkosi yakho (uAllâh) Yenze nkulu
  74,4,Iimpahla zakho uzicoce
  74,5,Ubumdaka ubuphephe (unqulo lwezithixo)
  74,6,Ungenzi inceba ufune engaphezulu (kunayo) wena
  74,7,Kodwa mayela neNkosi yakho yiba nomonde
  74,8,Ke kaloku lakuvuthelwa iXilongo
  74,9,Loo Mini iya kuba yiMini enzima
  74,10,Kwabangakholwayo ayiyi kuba lula
  74,11,Ndiyeke ke Mna nalowo Ndamdala NdiNdedwa
  74,12,Ndampha imfumba yobutyebi
  74,13,Nabantwana bekhona (kuye)
  74,14,"Ndandlala (into yonke) phambi kwakhe, Ndimenzela lula ubomi bakhe"
  74,15,Kanti usanqwenela ukuba Ndimongezelele ezinye
  74,16,Nakanye! Inene yena uye waba nendelelo mayela neeVesi zeThu
  74,17,Mna Ndiya kumgubungela ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu
  74,18,Inene yena wacinga waqulunqa
  74,19,Makaqalekiswe ke ngendlela awaqulunqa ngayo
  74,20,Kwakhona makaqalekiswe ngendlela awaqulunqa ngayo
  74,21,Waphinda wacinga kwakhona
  74,22,Wafingi’iintshiya wakhangeleka enomsindo
  74,23,Wabuya umva ekhukhumele
  74,24,"Wathi: “Le (‘Kur’ân) asinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ngumlingo obonelwe kubantu bakudala"
  74,25,Le asinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba lilizwi lomntu!”
  74,26,Mna ke Ndiya kumqhubela eSa’kar1 (eMlilweni wesiHogo)
  74,27,Yintoni na engakwenza wazi ukuba iyintoni na iSa’kar
  74,28,"Ayishiyi nto kuyo, ingashiyi nto (ingayitshisanga)"
  74,29,Ijika (yenze mnyama) izikhumba
  74,30,Phezu kwayo (iSa’kar) lishumi elinethoba (leengelosi)
  74,31,"Ke kaloku Asibenzanga abalindi boMlilo (wesiHogo) baba yinto yimbi ngaphandle kweengelosi. Kananjalo Asilenzanga layinto yimbi inani lazo ngaphandle kokuba libe luvavanyo lwabo bangakholwayo kwanokuba abo babenikwe isiBhalo baqonde baneliseke kwanokuba abo bakholwayo bande elukholweni nabo babenikwe isiBhalo namakholwa bangabi nakuthandabuza kwanokuba abo bantliziyo zabo zinesifo (abahanahanisi) nabangakholwayo bathi: “Uthetha ukuthini na uAllâh ngawo lo mzekelo?” Ngolo hlobo ke uAllâh Ulahlekisa lowo Athande ukumlahlekisa Akhokele lowo Athande ukumkhokela. Ukanti akukho namnye owaziyo amajoni eNkosi yakho ngaphadle kwaYo. Ke kaloku (ukukhankanywa koMlilo) akunto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba yinkumbuzo ebabantwini"
  74,32,Nakanye! (Ndifunga) ngenyanga
  74,33,Nangobusuku xa busimka
  74,34,Nangentseni xa iba mhlophe
  74,35,"Inene wona [uMlilo (yintuthumbiso)] enkulu"
  74,36,Unjengesilumkiso kubantu
  74,37,Khona ukuze lowo uthandayo phakathi kwenu aqhubeke (nokukholwa) okanye ahlale phantsi (engakholwa)
  74,38,Wonkeumphefumlouyakubanjwangaloontouyisebenzeleyo
  74,39,Ngaphandle kwamadlelane okunene
  74,40,"Aya kuba seMiyezweni, ebuzana"
  74,41,Ngabaphuli-mthetho
  74,42,"(Ebabuza okokuba): Yintoni na enifake eSa’kar?”"
  74,43,"Baya kuthi bona: “Sasingengabo abanye babo babethandaza"
  74,44,Sasingondli namahlwempu
  74,45,"Kananjalo\tsasidla\tngokuthetha\tamampunge\t(ngabo babethandaza)"
  74,46,Kwaye sasidla ngokuyiphika iMini yembuyekezo
  74,47,“Sada safikelwa kukufa okwakungathandabuzeki.”
  74,48,Ngoko ke ayiyi kubanceda nto intethelelo yabo nabaphi na abathetheleli
  74,49,Yintoni kanye ngabo le nto bayitshikilelayo inkumbuzo
  74,50,Babe ngathi ziimbongolo zasendle ezothukileyo
  74,51,Ezibaleka ingonyama
  74,52,Ukusuka apho umntu ngamnye kubo unqwenela ukuba anikwe isiBhalo esele sandlaliwe
  74,53,Nakanye! Kodwa bona abanaloyiko loBomi oBuzayo
  74,54,Nakanye! Inene yona (i’Kur’ân) yinkumbuzo
  74,55,Ke kaloku lowo ufunayo uya kuyikhumbula
  74,56,"Kananjalo abayi kukhumbula nto ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande ukuba bakukhumbule. Yena Ufanelwe kukoyikwa, Wanele ukuba Axolele"
  75,1,Ndifunga ngeMini yoVuko
  75,2,Nangomphefumlo okhalimayo
  75,3,Ingaba umntu (lo) ucinga ukuba Asiyi kuwadibanisa na amathambo akhe
  75,4,Ewe nje Siyakwazi Thina nokumisa ngendlela iintupha zeminwe yakhe
  75,5,Kodwa umntu unqwenela ukuqhubekela phambili nokwenza isono
  75,6,"(Ude) abuze: “Inini na iMini YoVuko?”"
  75,7,Ke kaloku xa ukubona2 (kwabo) kuphandliwe
  75,8,Nenyanga iba mnyama
  75,9,Ilanga nenyanga zidityanisiwe
  75,10,"Umntu uya kuthi ngalooMini: “Iphi na indawo yokubalekela?”"
  75,11,Nakanye! Akuyi kubakho ndawo yakhuseleko
  75,12,ENkosini yakho ngaloo Mini kuya kubakho (indawo yokuphumla) yanaphakade
  75,13,"Umntu ngaloo Mini uya kuchazelwa ngoko wakhokelisa ngako (okuzizenzo) nawakunkonyayo, (akanikela ngako)"
  75,14,Ke kaloku umntu uya kuba lingqina (elaneleyo) ngokuchasene nesiqu sakhe
  75,15,Kanti nokuba sele ezithethelela
  75,16,"(Wena ke Muhammad) unganyakazisi ulwimi lwakho ngayo3 (i’Kur’ân), ungxame ngayo"
  75,17,InenekuxhomekekekuThiukuqokelelwakwayo(entliziyweni yakho) nokucengcelezwa kwayo
  75,18,Ke kaloku SiSakuyicengceleza (ngoJibrîl) wena landela ucengcelezo lwayo
  75,19,Kananjalo kukuThi ukucaciswa kwayo (kuwe)
  75,20,Nakanye! Nina (bantu) nithanda ukungxamela obu bomi
  75,21,Nibuyeke uBomi oBuzayo
  75,22,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kukhazimla
  75,23,Bejonge eNkosini yabo
  75,24,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kumatsheka (buxwebe)
  75,25,Belindele ukuba baza kuhlelwa lilishwa phezu kwabo
  75,26,"Nakanye! Xa umphefumlo ufika kugovane, (kofayo)"
  75,27,"Kuye kuthiwe: “Ngubani na oza kumphilisa (amsindise ekufeni)?”"
  75,28,Ke kaloku yena (ofayo) uye aqonde okokuba (sele ilixesha lakhe) lokuhamba (kulo mhlaba)
  75,29,"Kananjalo\tomnye\tumlenze\tuye\tudityaniswe\tnomnye [wambathiswe ingubo yokufa (ikafan]"
  75,30,Ihambo ngaloo Mini ibhekisa eNkosini yakho (uAllâh)
  75,31,Ngoko ke ongakholwayo akazanga anikele (kumalizo) engazanga wathandaza nakuthandaza
  75,32,Kodwa endaweni yoko waphika watshikila
  75,33,Emva koko waya kubantu bakubo ehamba ngokuzingca (ngokuqhayisa)
  75,34,"Yeha kuwe (mntu ungakholwayo), yeha"
  75,35,"Kwakhona yeha kuwe mntu ungakholawayo, yeha"
  75,36,Umntu (lo) ucinga ukuba uza kuyekwa yedwa angahoywa na
  75,37,Wayengazanga waba liqabaza elivela kulwelo lwembewu yomntu na
  75,38,"Waza waba lihlwili elinamatheleyo, uAllâh Wadala isimo sakhe Wamlinganisela"
  75,39,"Wazangayewenzaabalinganeababini, oyindodanowasetyhini"
  75,40,Ingaba loo (Mdali) akakwazi ukunika bomi kwabafileyo na
  76,1,Ingaba akuzanga khe kubekho xesha na emntwini apho waye eyinto engafanelanga kukhankanywa na
  76,2,Inene Samdala UMntu ngomxube weqabaza lembewu yomntu khon’ukuze Simvavanye; kananjalo Samenzela ukuva nokubona
  76,3,"Samkhokela eNdleleni, nokuba uyabulela na okanye akabuleli"
  76,4,Kananjalo Silungiselele abangakholwayo amakhonkco namakhamandela neDangatya
  76,5,Inene wona amalungisa aya kusela indebe (yewayini) exutywe neKâfûr
  76,6,Umthombo ekuza kusela izicaka zika-Allâh ezingamalungisa (kwaye); ziwenza umpompoze ungaphezi
  76,7,Abo ke ngabo bazalisekisa izifungo zabo boyike neMini ekungcola kwayo kuya kuba banzi
  76,8,"Kananjalo bona bapha (abanye) ukutya nangona nabo bekuthanda (kodwa bakunike) abahlwempuzekileyo, noyinkedama, nongumthinjwa"
  76,9,"(Besithi): “Sinondlela ukukholisa uAllâh, asinqweneli mvuzo nambulelo kuni"
  76,10,"Inene thina soyika iMini enzima evela eNkosini yethu nephethe unxunguphalo, eya kwenza ubuso bubonakale busoyikeka.”"
  76,11,"Ngoko ke uAllâh uya kubasindisa bona ebubini baloo Mini, Abaphe ukukhanya kobuhle nolonwabo"
  76,12,"Kananjalo imbuyekezo yabo iya kuba yiPaladesi, nezambatho zesilika ngenxa yokuba kaloku bona baba nomonde"
  76,13,"(Bona baya kuba) behleli zava ezihlalweni zabo (ezimfuma- mfuma), abayi kubona langa nangqele apho"
  76,14,"Ngentla kufutshane nabo iya kuba yimithunzi yayo [iPaladesi (neziqhamo)] zayo ukuba bazinqothule, ziya kuthotyelwa ezantsi ukuba zivumele (ukunqothulwa)"
  76,15,Kananjalo kuya kuhanjiswa phakathi kwabo izitya neendebe eziya kuba zidalwe zacwenga
  76,16,Iigilasi ezicwengileyo ezenziwe ngesilivere ezimlinganiselo wazo wenziwe ngabo
  76,17,Kananjalo baya kunikwa indebe (yewayini) exutywe nejinja (ginger)
  76,18,"(Basele), kumthombo ophakathi (ePaladesi) obizwa ngokuba yiSalsabîl"
  76,19,Kuya kuba kuhamba-hamba amakhwenkwana enziwe ngonaphakade. Xa uwabona ungacinga ukuba aziiperile ezisarhaziweyo
  76,20,Naxa ujonga apho (ePaladesi) uya kubona ubumnandi nobungangamsha (bokwenene)
  76,21,"Baya kwambathiswa izambatho eziluhlaza zesilika esulungekileyo, engqindilili. Kananjalo baya kuhonjiswa ngezacholo zesilivere Ize iNkosi yabo Ibanike isiselo esihlambululayo"
  76,22,"(Kananjalo kuya kuthiwa): “Inene oku kuni ngumvuzo kananjalo, umzamo wenu uyabulelwa.”"
  76,23,"Inene SiThi Abathumele i’Kur’ân kuwe (Muhammad), amathuba ngamathuba"
  76,24,"Yiba nomonde ke ngesigqibo seNkosi yakho, ungathobeli (nawuphi na) umoni phakathi kwabo okanye ongenambulelo"
  76,25,Ke kaloku khumbula igama leNkosi yakho (emthandazweni) ekuseni nangokuhlwa
  76,26,Nasebusuku qubuda kuYo uYizukise ngobusuku (obo)
  76,27,"Inene abo [bangakholwayo (baleqa)], bathande ubomi balo mhlaba beshiya ngemva kwabo iMini ebuhlungu"
  76,28,"SiThi ababadalayo Sabomeleza izimo zabo, kanti Sithanda Singayijika imbonakalo yabo ngotshintsho (olwahluke) kwaphela"
  76,29,"Inene le Vesi (ye‘Kur’ân) isisiyalo, ngoko ke lowo uthandayo makazithabathele iNdlela eya eNkosini yakhe"
  76,30,"Ukanti nina aningekhe nikwazi, ngaphandle kokuba kuthande uAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguSolwazi nguSobulumko"
  76,31,Yena Uya kungenisa kwinceba yaKhe lowo Amthandileyo. Abenzi bobubi ke bona Ubalungiselele isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  77,1,(Ndifunga) ngemimoya ethunyelwa phambili omnye emva komnye
  77,2,Nangemimoya evuthuza ngamandla
  77,3,Nangemimoya echitha-chitha amafu nemvula
  77,4,NangeeVesi ze’Kur’ân ezahlula okulungileyo kokugwenxa
  77,5,Nangeengelosi ezizisa isiTyhilelo kubaProfeti
  77,6,Ukunqamla konke ukuzithethelela zilumkise nokulumkisa
  77,7,Inene oko nikuthenjisiweyo kunyanzelekile kwenzeke
  77,8,Xa iinkwenkwezi ziphelelwe kukukhanya kwazo
  77,9,Naxa izulu licandeka
  77,10,Naxa iintaba ziphaphatheke zemka
  77,11,"Naxa\tabaThunywa\tbehlanganiselwe\tixesha\tlabo elikhethiweyo"
  77,12,Yiyiphi le Mini le miqondiso irhoxiselwa yona
  77,13,(Irhoxiselwa) iMini yohlenga-hlengiso
  77,14,Yintoni na enokukwenza wazi ukuba iyintoni na iMini yohlengahlengiso
  77,15,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,16,ASizanga Sibatshabalalise na abamandulo
  77,17,Siya kwenza njalo ke nangezizukulwana zamva ukulandelisa
  77,18,Siqubisana kanjalo ke naboni
  77,19,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,20,ASizanga Sinidale ngolwelo olonyanyekayo na
  77,21,Saza Salubeka kwindawo yalo yokhuseleko (esibelekweni)
  77,22,Ixesha elingummiselo owaziwayo
  77,23,"Samisela ixesha elithile ngalo, (SiThi ke) abaMiseli xesha Abalungileyo"
  77,24,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,25,Asiwenzanga umhlaba waba sisiqulathi
  77,26,Sabaphilileyo nabaFileyo na
  77,27,Saza Sabeka apho kuwo iintaba ezinde eziqinileyo. Saninika amanzi amnandi ukuba nisele
  77,28,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,29,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yiyani koko nanidla ngokuphika"
  77,30,Yiyani ethunzini (lomsi woMlillo wesiHogo) oziingqimba ezintathu
  77,31,"(Kodwa) lingenamthunzi upholileyo, lingancedi nakunceda ngokuchasene neDangatya.”"
  77,32,"Inene\twona\tloo\t(msi)\tutakisa\tiintlantsi\t(ezinkulu) ezingangenqaba (yamajoni)"
  77,33,Ngathi ziinkamela ezilubhelu bumnyama
  77,34,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,35,Le yiMini abangayi kuthetha ngayo
  77,36,Bengayi kuvunyelwa nakuvunyelwa ukuba bazithethelele
  77,37,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,38,"Le\tyiMini\tyoMgwebo;\tSiya\tkuba\tSinihlanganisile nabamandulo"
  77,39,"Ukuba ngaba ninalo icebo, cebani kaloku ngokuchasene naM (ngoku)"
  77,40,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,41,"Inene\tabanyulu\tbaya\tkuba\tphakathi\tkwemithunzi nemithombo"
  77,42,Neziqhamo (zohlobo) abalufunayo
  77,43,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yidlani nisele nanele ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  77,44,Inene Thina sibavuza kajalo ke abenzi bokulungileyo
  77,45,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,46,"(Hini na nina bangakholwayo), yibani nisitya nizonwabise okwethutyana inene nina ningaboni"
  77,47,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,48,"Ukanti xa kusithiwa kubo: Gobani amadolo (phambi koAllâh)”, abagobi bona"
  77,49,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,50,Yiyiphi ke enye intetho emva (kwe’Kur’ân) abaya kukholwa kuyo
  78,1,Kungantoni na oko baphikisana ngako
  78,2,KungeeNdaba ezinkulu
  78,3,Ezo bangenakuvumelana ngazo
  78,4,"Yeha, inene kungekudala baza kwazi"
  78,5,"Kwakhona yeha, inene kungekudala baza kwazi"
  78,6,"ASiwenzanga\tumhlaba\twaba\tngumphangalalo owandlalekileyo na"
  78,7,Neentaba1 zaba zizikhonkwane
  78,8,Saza Sanidala ngambini
  78,9,Senza ukulala kwenu (kwaba lixesha) lokuphumla
  78,10,Senza ubusuku isigqumathelo
  78,11,Senza imini ixesha lokuxelengela ukuphila
  78,12,Sakha phezu kwenu amazulu asixhenxe omeleleyo
  78,13,Sabeka apho isibane esikhazimlayo
  78,14,Sathoba amanzi ngobuninzi emafini emvula
  78,15,Ukuze ngawo Sivelise imbewu nezityalo
  78,16,Nemiyezo eshinyeneyo
  78,17,Inene iMini yohlenga-hlengiso yinto esele imiselwe kakade
  78,18,"Mini leyo, iXilongo liya kuvuthelwa nize nibuyiswe niziindimbane"
  78,19,Namazulu avuleke ngokungathi ziingcango
  78,20,Neentaba zithi shwaka ngokungathi yinkohliso
  78,21,Inene isiHogo sihleli sincathamile
  78,22,Likhaya lokuhlala abo bangabagabadeli (abenzi bezono)
  78,23,Baya kuhlala apho kuso iminyaka ngeminyaka
  78,24,"Akukho nto ipholileyo baya kukuyingcamla apho, kungekho nasiselo na kakade"
  78,25,"Ngaphandle kolwelo3 olubilayo, nobubomvu"
  78,26,Umvuzo ofanelekileyo (waboni)
  78,27,Kuba abazanga boyike kufakwa ngxoxweni (ngezenzo zabo)
  78,28,Basuka bathabatha imiqondiso yeThu njengobuxoki
  78,29,Kwaye yonke into Siyigcinile eNcwadini
  78,30,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ke iziqhamo (zezenzo zenu) kuba akukho songezelelo eSiya kuninika sona ngaphandle kwesohlwayo!”"
  78,31,"Inene, kumalungisa iya kuba yimpumelelo"
  78,32,"IMiyezo ebiyelweyo, nemidiliya"
  78,33,neentombi ezibudala bulinganayo
  78,34,Nendebe ezele qhu
  78,35,Akukho mampunge baya kuwava apho nabuxoki
  78,36,Umvuzo ophuma eNkosini yakho. Isipho esaneleyo
  78,37,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, nako konke okuphakathi kuwo, uSolubabalo; Akukho namnye oya kuba nagunya lakuthetha naYe"
  78,38,"IMini apho uMoya (oyiNgcwele) neengelosi ziya kuma ngemigca. Akukho namnye oya kuthetha ngaphandle kwalowo uya kuvunyelwa nguSozinceba, yaye uya kuthetha okulungileyo kuphela"
  78,39,"Leyo\tyiMini\tyeNyaniso!\tNgako\toko\tlowo\tufunayo makathabathe ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yakhe"
  78,40,"Inene Sinilumkisile ngesohlwayo esikufuphi. Mini leyo umntu aya kuzibona izenzo zezandla zakhe, aze athi umchasi- kholo: “Yeha kum! Akwaba bendiluthuli"
  79,1,"Ndifunga\tngezo\t(ngelosi)\tzirhola\t(imiphefumlo yabangcolileyo), ngokurhabaxa"
  79,2,Nangezo zirhola (imiphefumlo yamalungisa) ngocoselelo
  79,3,"Nangezo ziphaphazela, zindande (zithunywa imiyalezo yenceba)"
  79,4,Zingxamele phambili ngokungathi ziselugqatsweni
  79,5,Zide zicwangcise (imiyalelo yeNkosi yazo) (xa kukhala iXilongo)
  79,6,"NgeMini\tukuvuthelwa\t(kweXilongo\tlokuqala)\tkuya kudlokovisa (indalo)"
  79,7,Kulandele intshukumo emva kwentshukumo (xa kukhala elesibini)
  79,8,Iintliziyo ziya kubetha kabuhlungu ngaloo Mini
  79,9,Amehlo abe buthathaka (ondele phantsi)
  79,10,"Bathi: “Ingaba ngenene siza kubuyiselwa kwimo yethu yamandulo na"
  79,11,Nokuba sele singamathambo abolileyo?”
  79,12,"Bathi: “Okokuba kunjalo, kuya kuba kukubuya okunelahleko (oko).”"
  79,13,"Inene, iya kuba sisikhalo esinye (seXilongo)"
  79,14,"Yabonani, baya kutyekezelwa ngaphandle (kwamangcwaba abo)"
  79,15,Ingaba sele lifikile na ibali likaMûsâ kuwe
  79,16,"Xa\tiNkosi\tyakhe Yaye Yambiza\tkwintili\t(engcwele) yaseTuwâ"
  79,17,"(Yathi kuye): “Yiya kuFir’awn kuba sele egabadele!”"
  79,18,"Uthi kuye: “Akungethandi na ukuhlambuluka ezonweni"
  79,19,Nokuba ndikukhokelele eNkosini yakho ukuze uYoyike?”
  79,20,Ngoko (UMûsâ) wambonisa umqondiso omkhulu
  79,21,"Kodwa uFir’awn akawamkela umqondiso, akasithobela nesikhokelo"
  79,22,"Emvakokowatshikila,wafulathelawazabalaza(ngokuchasene nomyalezo kaMûsâ)"
  79,23,"Wahlanganisa abantu bakhe, wenza isimemezo"
  79,24,"Wathi: “Mna ndiyinkosi yenu ephezulu”"
  79,25,"Kodwa uAllâh Wamhlasela, Wenza umzekelo ngaye kobu bomi nakuBomi oBuzayo"
  79,26,Inene kule mbali kukho isifundo sakhe nabani na omoyikayo uAllâh
  79,27,Kunzima na ukudala nina kunezulu eliphezulu Alakhileyo
  79,28,"Uluphakamisile uphahla lwalo, Walicwangcisa, Walinika imfezeko"
  79,29,Ugqume ubusuku balo ngobumnyama Wavelisa imini yalo ngokukhanya
  79,30,Emva koko Wandlala umhlaba
  79,31,Waza apho kuwoWavelisa amanzi wawo nedlelo lawo
  79,32,Ukanti iintaba zona Uzigxumeke zaqina nkqi
  79,33,(Ukuze apho kuphume) isixhaso senu nemfuyo yenu
  79,34,Ke kaloku kwakufika intlekele enkulu
  79,35,Mini leyo umntu aza kuyikhumbula into abe eyizabalazela
  79,36,Ukanti uMlilo wesiHogo uya kubonakaliswa uthi thaa (kumntu wonke) obonayo
  79,37,Ke lowo ungumgabadeli (umenzi wobubi)
  79,38,Owakhetha ubomi beli hlabathi (elandela iminqweno yakhe kunentando ka-Allâh)
  79,39,Inene ikhaya lakhe liya kuba nguMlilo wesiHogo
  79,40,"Kodwa yena lowo waye waba noloyiko lokumiswa phambi kweNkosi yakhe (uAllâh), wazoyisa ekulandeleni iinkanuko zakhe ezikukungcola"
  79,41,Inene iPaladesi iya kuba likhaya lakhe
  79,42,"Wena (Muhammad) bakubuza ngeYure (bathi): liya kuba nini na ilixa (lokuzalisekiswa) kwayo"
  79,43,Ayiloxanduva lwakho ukuzalisekiswa kwayo
  79,44,Inzaliseko yayo ixhomekeke eNkosini yakho
  79,45,Inene wena unguMlumkisi kulowo uyoyikayo
  79,46,Mhla bayibona (iya kuba ngathi) baphile (kulo mhlaba) injikalanga yayo okanye intsasa yayo (kuphela)
  80,1,"(UMprofeti) Wafing’iintshiya, wafulathela"
  80,2,Kuba kweza kuye indoda eyimfama
  80,3,Kodwa yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba ngebhaqo nayo ibinokufumana ukuhlambuluka
  80,4,okanye yamkele ululeko nenkumbuzo ukuze ibe luncedo kuyo
  80,5,Hayi lowo uzicingela ukuba akaxhomekanga (kuAllâh)
  80,6,Wena usuka uhoye yena
  80,7,Nangona ingeloxanduva lwakho ukumhlambulula
  80,8,Kodwa yena lowo uze kuwe ebaleka
  80,9,Enoloyiko (lwesohlwayo sika-Allâh entliziyweni yakhe)
  80,10,Awumnanzanga yena
  80,11,Nakanye! Kuba ngenene lo nguMyalezo oyinkumbuzo
  80,12,Ngoko ke othandayo makahlale ewukhumbula
  80,13,"UseziNcwadini ezibekekileyo, eziphethwe ngentlonipheko enkulu"
  80,14,"Ziphakamile (ngesidima, zigcinwe) ngcwele"
  80,15,"Ubhalwe ngezandla zabaBhali, (iingelosi)"
  80,16,"Abahloniphekileyo, abazithobileyo benobulungisa"
  80,17,Uqalekisiwe umtu ongakholwayo! (Kungani na ukuba angabi nambulelo kuAllâh)
  80,18,Yintoni kanti (uAllâh) Amdale ngayo
  80,19,"(Umdale)\tngeqabaza\tlembewu\tyomntu!\tWamdala wazaWamlinganisela ngokwemfanelo"
  80,20,Waphinda Wamenzela lula indlela yakhe (yokuba azalwe)
  80,21,"Waphinda kwakhona Wamenza ukuba afe, angcwatywe"
  80,22,"Kwakhona ngokwentando yaKhe, Uya kumbuyisela ebomini"
  80,23,Inene umntu akakwenzanga oko Amyalele kona
  80,24,Ngoko ke umntu makakhe aqwalasele ukutya kwakhe
  80,25,Sithulula amanzi (emvula) ngobuninzi
  80,26,Size Siqhekeze umhlaba ube ngamasuntswana
  80,27,Senze iinkozo (zembewu) zihlume (izithombo) kuwo
  80,28,Imidiliya nefula (yokutyiwa yimfuyo)
  80,29,Neminquma namasundu
  80,30,NeMiyezo enemithi eshinyeneyo
  80,31,Neziqhamo namadlelo
  80,32,(Ukuba zibe) sisixhaso senu nemfuyo yenu
  80,33,Kodwa yakufika ingxolo (ukukhala kweXilongo okwesibini ngeMini yoVuko)
  80,34,Ngaloo Mini umntu uya kubaleka ashiye umntakwabo
  80,35,Nomama wakhe notata wakhe
  80,36,Nomfazi wakhe nabantwana bakhe
  80,37,"Ngaloo Mini umntu ngamnye uya kuxakeka zezakhe, angazihoyi ezabanye"
  80,38,Ngaloo Mini ubuso babanye buya kukhazimla (bube buhle)
  80,39,"Behleka, bevuyiswa ziindaba ezimnandi"
  80,40,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kuzala luthuli bumbatshe
  80,41,Bugqunywe bubumnyama
  80,42,"Abo ngabangakholwayo, abangcolileyo, (abakrexezayo)"
  81,1,Xa ilanga lisongwa (licinywa ukukhanya)
  81,2,Naxa iinkwenkwezi zisiwa
  81,3,Naxa iintaba zenziwe zanyamalala
  81,4,Naxa iinkamela ezimithiyo zingasahoywanga
  81,5,Naxa izilo zasendle ziqokelelwe ndawonye
  81,6,Naxa iilwandle zinga zidwanguza amadangatya omlilo ziphuphuma
  81,7,Naxa imiphefumlo ihlanganiswa nemizimba yayo
  81,8,Naxa (usana) oluyintombazana olwangcwatywa luphila lubuzwa
  81,9,“Sono sini na elabulawelwa sona?”
  81,10,"Naxa\tamaphepha\t(abhaliweyo)\t[ezenzo\tezilungileyo (nezingcolileyo) zomntu ngamnye] etyhilwa elubala"
  81,11,Naxa isibhakabhaka sihlutyulwa sisuswa endaweni yaso
  81,12,Naxa uMlilo wesiHogo uphenjwa
  81,13,Naxa iPaladesi isondezelwa kufutshane
  81,14,(Ngoko) umntu ngamnye uya kuyazi into ayivelisileyo (elungileyo nengalunganga)
  81,15,Yeha! Ndifunga ngezijikelezi-langa (iiplanethi) eziphinda zihlehle
  81,16,Nangezijikelezilanga ezihamba ngokubaleka ziye kusithela
  81,17,Nangobusuku xa buphela
  81,18,Nangentseni xa ikhanya
  81,19,"Inene eli liLizwi (i’Kur’ân eliziswe) sisiThunywa esihloniphekileyo (uJibrîl, evela kuAllâh, esiza kuMprofeti uMuhammad)"
  81,20,"Esinamandla, (nobungangamsha), siphuma (kuAllâh), iNkosi yeTrone (engenakushukunyiswa yinto ngaphandle kwentando yaKhe)"
  81,21,"(UJibrîl, isithunywa) Esithotyelwayo (ziingelosi zamazulu), sikwathembekile"
  81,22,Hini na bantu! Ugxa wenu (uMuhammad) akaphambenanga
  81,23,Ngokwenene yena wambona uJibrîl elundini olucacileyo
  81,24,kwaye yena akalubandezi ulwazi (lwezinto) eziyimfihlakalo
  81,25,Ukanti (le ‘Kur’ân) ayilolizwi likaShaytân (uSathana) owaqalekiswayo
  81,26,Ngoku ke nina nisingise phi
  81,27,"Inene\tle\t(‘Kur’ân)\tayinto\tyimbi\tngaphandle\tkokuba yinkumbuzo kwindalo yonke"
  81,28,Kuye nabani na kuni ofuna ukuhamba ngokuthe tye
  81,29,"Yaye aninako ukuzithandela (ukuhamba ngokuthe tye) ngaphandle kokuba kuthande uAllâh, iNkosi yamaphakade"
  82,1,Xa isibhakabhaka sicandeka phakathi
  82,2,Naxa iinkwenkwezi zisiwa
  82,3,Naxa iilwandle ziphuphuma
  82,4,Naxa amangcwaba ebhedululiwe
  82,5,"Umphefumlo\t(ngamnye)\tuya\tkuyazi\tinto\toze\tnayo ngaphambili noyishiye ngemva"
  82,6,"Hini na wena mntu! Yintoni na ekwenze akwaYihoya iNkosi yakho, uSobubele"
  82,7,"Eyakudalayo\tYakubumba\tngemfezeko\tngomlinganiselo onguwo"
  82,8,Nayiphi na imo Ethanda ukuba ube yiyo wena; Ikudibanisa ube njalo
  82,9,Yeha inene nina niyawuphika uMgwebo
  82,10,"Inene\tphezu\tkwenu\tkukho\t(iingelosi\tezinyulelwe) ukunilondoza"
  82,11,"zilunge kakhulu, zihloniphekile, zibhala phantsi (konke) enikwenzayo"
  82,12,Zikwazi konke enikwenzayo
  82,13,Inene amalungisa aya kuba selonwabeni
  82,14,Inene abangcolileyo baya kuba seMlilweni wesiHogo
  82,15,Baya kungena kuso apho ngoMhla wemivuzo
  82,16,Yaye abasokuze bakwazi ukuphuncula kuso
  82,17,Yintoni na enokukucacisela ukuba uMhla wemivuzo (lo) uyintoni na
  82,18,"Kwakhona\tyintoni\tna\tenokukucacisela\tukuba\tuMhla wemivuzo (lo) uyintoni na"
  82,19,Iya kuba yiMini apho kungekho mphefumlo uya kuba namandla akwenzela nto omnye. Yaye ulawulo ngaloo Mini luya kuba loluka-Allâh (lonke)
  83,1,Yeha kwabo banobuqhetseba
  83,2,"Abo bathi xa kufuneka befumene into kwabanye abantu, bafune umlinganiselo ozeleyo"
  83,3,"Kodwa xa kufuneka ibe ngabo amabanike abanye abantu umlinganiselo onguwo, suke bona babanike omncinane kunofanelekileyo"
  83,4,Abacingi na ukuba baza kuphinda bavuswe (baxoxiswe)
  83,5,NgoMhla oMkhulu
  83,6,UMhla abaya kuthi bonke abantu bame phambi kweNkosi yamazwe
  83,7,"Yeha inene, imibhalo yezenzo zabangcolileyo igcinwe kwi- Sijjîn"
  83,8,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba iyintoni na iSijjiîn
  83,9,YiNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  83,10,Yeha kwabo baphikayo ngaloo Mini
  83,11,Abo baphika iMini yoMgwebo
  83,12,Akakho oyiphikayo ngaphandle komoni ogabadeleyo
  83,13,"Lowo uthi xa efundelwa iziTyhilelo zeThu athi: “Ziintsomi zamandulo”"
  83,14,Nakanye! (Banongcoliseko) lomhlwa ezintliziyweni zabo ngenxa yezenzo zabo
  83,15,Inene baya kusithwa bangayiboni iNkosi yabo ngaloo Mini
  83,16,"Kwakhona, inene baya kuphoswa eMlilweni wesiHogo"
  83,17,"Yaye kuya kuthiwa (kubo): “Le yilaa (nyaniso) naniyiphika!”"
  83,18,Inene iiNcwadi zezenzo zamalungisa zigcinwe kwi- ‘Iliyyûn
  83,19,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba iyintoni na i-’Iliyyûn
  83,20,YiNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  83,21,Engqinwa ngabasondele kuAllâh
  83,22,Inene amalungisa aya kuba selonwabeni
  83,23,"Ehleli ezihlalweni eziphakamileyo, emana ukujonga-jonga, (ebukela ubuhle bezinto eziseMyezweni)"
  83,24,Uya kubona inkazimlo yochulumanco ebusweni bawo
  83,25,"Unxano\tlwawo\tluya\tkuqatyulwa\tngewayini\tenyulu, etywiniweyo"
  83,26,"Etywina\tlayo\tliziziqholo\tzeMisk1:\tNantsi\tke\tinto abanomnqweno abanokukhuphisana ngayo"
  83,27,Ixutywe namanzi omthombo weTasnîm. okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongasokuze ube nasiphelo
  83,28,Umthombo ekusela kuwo abo bakufuphi no Allâh
  83,29,"Inene, aboni babedla ngokubahleka abo bakholwayo"
  83,30,"Ngalo lonke ixesha begqitha ecaleni kwabo (bakholwayo), baqobelane amehlo (begculela)"
  83,31,Bathi bakufika kumawabo benze intlekisa
  83,32,"Baze bathi lonke ixesha xa bebabona bathi: “Yabonani! Aba bantu balahlekile ngenene!”"
  83,33,Ukanti babengathunywanga ukuba babe ngabalondolozi babo
  83,34,"Ngale\tMini\tngabakholwayo\tabaya\tkuba\tbehleka abangakholwayayo"
  83,35,"Behleli ezihlalweni (ezimfuma-mfuma), eziphakamileyo, bejonga-jonga"
  83,36,"Abamelanga\tkubuyekezwa\tna\tabangakholwayo\tngoko bakwenzayo"
  84,1,Xa isibhakabhaka sisahlukana phakathi
  84,2,"Siphulaphule, sithobele iNkosi yaso yaye kunyanzelekile senze njalo"
  84,3,Naxa umhlaba usanekwa
  84,4,Sele utyekezele ngaphandle konke oko bekungaphakathi kuwo
  84,5,"Uphulaphula, uthobela iNkosi yawo yaye unyanzelekile wenze njalo"
  84,6,"Hini na wena mntu! Inene, wena Uya kubuyela eNkosini yakho nezenzo zakho (oko) kukubuyela okungathandabuzekiyo"
  84,7,Lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe (yezenzo) ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  84,8,Inene lowo kungekudala ityala lakhe liya kuxoxwa ngokulula
  84,9,Aze abuyele kwabakubo evuya
  84,10,Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe ngemva
  84,11,Uya kuthandazela ukuba atshabalale
  84,12,"Yaye uya kungena eMlilweni odwanguzayo, aviswe ukutshisa kwawo"
  84,13,Kaloku yena wayonwabile phakathi kwabakubo
  84,14,Eneneni yena wayecinga ukuba asokuze abuyele (kuThi)
  84,15,Kanti! INkosi yakhe Yayihleli Imqwalasele
  84,16,Ngoko ke Ndifunga ngokukhazimla kokutshona kwelanga
  84,17,Nangobusuku nako konke obukuqokelela ngobumnyama babo
  84,18,Nangenyanga xa ipheleleyo
  84,19,Niya kuhamba amanqanaba ngamanqanaba (kobu bomi nakuBomi oBuzayo)
  84,20,Kanti yintoni na ngabo ukuba bangakholwa
  84,21,Ukanti naxa i’Kurân icengcelezwa kubo abawi baqubude
  84,22,"Yeha\tabo\tbangakholwayo\tbayamphikisa\t(uMprofeti uMuhammad)"
  84,23,"Kanti\tYena\tuAllâh\tUkwazi\tkakuhle\tabakuqokelelayo (okuzizenzo ezilungileyo nezingcolileyo)"
  84,24,Vakalisa ke ngoko isohlwayo esibuhlungu kubo
  84,25,Ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo benze izenzo zobulungisa
  85,1,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka esibambe iinkwenkwezi ezinkulu
  85,2,NangeMini yesithembiso
  85,3,NangeMini yokungqina nangeMini1 engqinelwayo
  85,4,Baqalekisiwe abenza umsele
  85,5,Womlilo ogalelwe isivuthisi
  85,6,Behleli ecaleni kwawo (bebukele abo babetshiswa kuwo)
  85,7,Yaye baye baba ngamangqina oko babekwenza ngokuchasene nabakholwayo
  85,8,"Akukho tyala limbi ababelenzile (abakholwayo) ngaphandle kokukholwa kuAllâh, uSomandla, Ofanelwe ziindumiso zonke"
  85,9,Yena nguMnini bukumkani bamazulu nomhlaba! Yaye uAllâh UliNgqina ngaphezulu kwazo zonke izinto
  85,10,"(Inene abo batshutshisa amakholwa namakholwakazi ngokuwangcungcuthekisa) baze bangaguquki, baza kufumana isohlwayo sesiHogo, yaye baza kufumana isohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  85,11,"Inene abo bakholwayo baze benze izenzo zobulungisa, okwabo iya kuba yiMiyezo ekumpompoza amanzi ngaphantsi kwayo. Leyo iya kuba yimpumelelo enkulu"
  85,12,"Inene\t(wena\tMuhammad)\tisohlwayo\tseNkosi\tyakho sibuhlungu kakhulu"
  85,13,"Inene\t(iNkosi\tyakho)\tyiYo\tEqalayo,\t(ukudala) Yiyo negqibelayo"
  85,14,"Yaye Yona nguMxoleli, uSoluthando"
  85,15,"UMnini Trone, eZukileyo"
  85,16,NguMenzi wentando yaKhe
  85,17,Ingaba ibali lemikhosi lifikile na kuwe
  85,18,(Imikhosi ) kaFir’awn namaThamûd
  85,19,Yeha abangakholwayo bayaqhubeka nokuphikisa (uMprofeti uMuhammad) nomyalezo wakhe oyi-Islam
  85,20,Kodwa Yena uAllâh Ubarhangqele ngemva kwabo
  85,21,Inene le yi’Kur’ân ezukileyo
  85,22,Ibhalwe eCwecweni elilondoloziweyo
  86,1,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka nangondwendwe lwasebusuku (inkwenkwezi ekhazimla kakhulu)
  86,2,"Yintoni\tna\tenokukucacisela\tokokuba\tundwendwe lwasebusuku yintoni na"
  86,3,Yinkwenkwezi ekukhazimla kwayo kugqobhozelayo
  86,4,Umphefumlo ngamnye unomkhuseli phezu kwawo
  86,5,Ngoko ke umntu makajonge ukuba udalwe ngantoni na
  86,6,Udalwe ngamanzi atsawulayo
  86,7,Avela phakathi komqolo neembambo
  86,8,Inene uAllâh Uyakwazi ukuphinda ambuyisele (ebomini) kwakhona
  86,9,NgeMini apho iimfihlelo ziya kuvavanywa
  86,10,Ngoko (umntu) akayi kuba namandla engayi kuba namncedisi
  86,11,Ndifunga ngesibhakabhaka (esiza nemvula) siphindaphinde
  86,12,Nangomhlaba ocazulukayo (xa kuhluma uhlaza kuwo)
  86,13,Inene le (‘Kur’ân) liLizwi elihluza (inyani ebuxokini)
  86,14,Yaye asiyonto yokonwabisa
  86,15,Inene bona baqulunqa iyelenqe ngawe (Muhammad)
  86,16,Kanti naM (oku kwaM) Ndiqulunqa icebo (ngokuchasene nabo)
  86,17,"Khawubayekelele abangakholwayo, ubaphathe ngobunono okwethutyana"
  87,1,"Zukisa igama leNkosi, UMlondolozi, Ophakamileyo"
  87,2,"Odale, Wacwangcisa ngokupheleleyo"
  87,3,"Owise (umthetho), Wanika isiKhokelo"
  87,4,Ovelise amadlelo aluhlaza
  87,5,"Aphinde awaguqule, Awenze atshazwe"
  87,6,Siyakukufundisawena(Muhammadi’Kur’ân) ngamanqanaba ukuze ungalibali
  87,7,Ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande (ukuba ukulibale). Inene Yena Uyakwazi okubonakalayo nokungabonakaliyo
  87,8,Siya kukwenzela lula indlela yakho ukuze kube lula (ukushumayela i-Islam)
  87,9,Ngoko ke nika isilumkiso eluntwini kuba isilumkiso siluncedo
  87,10,Uya kusiphulaphula onoloyiko
  87,11,Kodwa asiyi kuhoywa ngonelishwa
  87,12,Yena lowo uya kungeniswa kuMlilokazi omkhulu
  87,13,Akayi kufa apho engayi kuphila
  87,14,Inene uyaphumelela ozihlambululayo
  87,15,"(Ohlala)\tekhumbula\tigama\tleNkosi\tyakhe\tathandaze nokuthandaza"
  87,16,Kodwa nina nikhetha ubomi beli hlabathi
  87,17,Nangona uBomi Obuzayo ibobona bulungileyo bungenaso nasiphelo
  87,18,Inene oku kukwiziBhalo zokuqala
  87,19,IziBhalo zikaIbrâhîm noMûsâ
  88,1,Ingaba iindaba zesiganeko (esikhulu) zifikile na kuwe
  88,2,"Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kudangala, (budane)"
  88,3,"Besebenze nzima, bediniwe. (ngenxa yokuzinikela kunqulo zithixo)"
  88,4,bangeniswe eMlilweni odwanguzayo
  88,5,Besezwa amanzi omthombo obilayo
  88,6,Akuyi kubakho kutya kwabo (apho) ngaphandle kwe- ‘Dhari’1 ekrakra
  88,7,"Engayi kubondla, ingayi kudambisa ndlala"
  88,8,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kuchulumanca
  88,9,Bevuyiswa yimizamo yabo
  88,10,EMyezweni ophakamileyo
  88,11,Apho bangayi kuphinda beve ntetho inabungozi nabudenge
  88,12,Apho kuya kubakho umthombo ompompozayo
  88,13,Apho kuya kubakho iitrone eziphakamileyo
  88,14,Neendebe esele zilungisiwe kakade
  88,15,Neemandlalo (ezitofo-tofo) esele zidwelisiwe
  88,16,Neenkukho ezimfuma-mfuma sele zandlaliwe
  88,17,Abaziqwalaseli na iinkamela ukuba zidalwe kanjani
  88,18,Nesibhakabhaka ukuba siphakanyiswe kanjani na
  88,19,Neentaba (ezi) ukuba zimile (zaqina kanjani)
  88,20,Nomhlaba (lo) ukuba wandlalwe kanjani na
  88,21,"Bakhumbuze ke (Muhammad), inene wena ungumkhumbuzi"
  88,22,Awungomyaleli wabo
  88,23,Ngaphandle kwalowo ujibilikayo alahle ukholo
  88,24,Yena uAllâh Uya kumohlwaya ngesohlwayo esikhulu
  88,25,Inene kuThi kulapho baza kubuyela khona
  88,26,Kananjalo inene kukuThi apho baza kuphendula khona
  89,1,Ndifunga ngoms’obomvu
  89,2,Nangobusuku1 obulishumi
  89,3,Nangoku(dalwe) ngambini nangokungumnqakathi
  89,4,Nangobusuku xa busimka
  89,5,Ingaba kwezi (zifungo) zingentla apha akukho bungqina baneleyo na kubantu abanengqiqo (ukuba bashenxe kuzo zonke iintlobo zezono)
  89,6,Awubonanga na (Muhammad) ukuba iNkosi yakho Yenza njani na ngabantu bakwa’Ad
  89,7,Abakwa-Iram (ababebade kakhulu) ngathi ziintsika
  89,8,Ekungazanga kuphinde kudalwe abafana nabo ezweni
  89,9,Kanti namaThamûd ayeqhekeza amatye entlanjeni (akhe imizi yawo)
  89,10,Nabantu bakwaFir’awn umnini zibonda
  89,11,"Abagabadela, batsiba imida ehlabathini"
  89,12,Kulo apho benza ubutshinga obugqithisileyo
  89,13,Ngoko ke iNkosi yakho yathulula phezu kwabo iintlobo ngeentlobo zezohlwayo ezibuhlungu
  89,14,Inene iNkosi yakho Ihlala Ibajongile
  89,15,"Ke kaloku umntu, Ithi iNkosi yakhe Isakumvavanya ngokumnika intlonipheko nendyebo, asuke athi: (ngokuzigwagwisa): “INkosi yam Indinike intlonipheko.”"
  89,16,"Kodwa Ithi Yakumvavanya ngokuthi Imnciphisele isixhaso sakhe, (aqale) athi: “INkosi yam Indincitshile.”"
  89,17,Nakanye! Nina anizixabisanga iinkedama
  89,18,Yaye anikhuthazani ngokondla abasweleyo
  89,19,Yaye nidla amafa abo onke ngokunyoluka
  89,20,Kwaye nithanda ubutyebi ngothando olugqithisileyo
  89,21,Nakanye! Xa umhlaba ucunyuzwe wangumgubo
  89,22,"NeNkosi\tyakho\tIze\tneengelosi\t(zimi)\tngokwemiqolo ngemiqolo"
  89,23,"NesiHogo siya kuziswa kufutshane ngaloo Mini. Ngaloo Mini umntu uya kukhumbula, kodwa loo nkumbulo iya kumnceda ntoni"
  89,24,"Uya kuthi: “Kwowu! Akwaba ndandizenzele imisebenzi elungileyo kwangaphambili (ukusindisa) ubomi bam"
  89,25,Ke kaloku ngaloo Mini akukho mntu uya kohlwaya ngohlobo Aya kohlwaya ngalo Yena (uAllâh)
  89,26,Akukho mntu uya kuqamangela abenzi (bobubi ngohlobo) Aya kuqamangela ngalo Yena
  89,27,"(Kuya kuthiwa kumntu okholiweyo): “Wena ke mphefumlo osekuphumleni nasekwanelisekeni okupheleleyo"
  89,28,"Buyela eNkosini yakho ukholisekile, uYikholisile (naYo)"
  89,29,Ngena ngoko phakathi kwezicaka zaM
  89,30,Ngena ke ePaladesi yaM.”
  90,1,Ndifunga ngesi sixeko (saseMakkah)
  90,2,Wena (Muhammad) ungummi okhululekileyo wesi sixeko
  90,3,Nangomzali nangoko akuzeleyo
  90,4,Inene umntu Simdalele ekubulalekeni
  90,5,Ucinga ukuba akakho onamandla ngaphezu kwakhe
  90,6,"(Ude) athi (eqhayisa): “Ndichithe ubutyebi (bam) obuninzi!”"
  90,7,Ucinga ukuba akakho ombonayo na
  90,8,Asimenzelanga amehlo amabini na
  90,9,Nolwimi nemilebe emibini
  90,10,Sambonisa iindlela ezimbini (eliqhina nehlayo)
  90,11,"Kodwa akazamanga, ukalinyuka iqhina"
  90,12,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba liyintoni na iqhina
  90,13,Kukukhulula ikhoboka
  90,14,Okanye ukondla (abantu) ngemini yendlala
  90,15,(Ukondla) inkedama esondeleyo (kuwe ngokuzalana)
  90,16,Okanye ihlwempu eliqhwanda uthuli. (ngenxa yentlupheko)
  90,17,Aze abe ngomnye wabo bakholwayo (kwi-Islam) abathi bakhuthazane ukunyamezela nomonde. Bakhuthazane kananjalo ngokuba nyulu nangokuba nemfesane
  90,18,Bona abo ngabo bangasekunene (abahlali basePaladesi)
  90,19,"Ke bona abo bangakholwayo kwiiVesi zeThu, (ze`Kur’ân) bona ngabo bangasekhohlo (abahlali basesiHogweni)"
  90,20,UMlilo uya kubagubungela
  91,1,Ndifunga ngelanga nangokumenyezela kwalo
  91,2,Nangenyanga xa ililandela
  91,3,Nangemini xa ibonisa ukukhazimla kwalo (ilanga)
  91,4,Nangobusuku xa buligquma
  91,5,Nangezulu nangaloWo Walakhayo
  91,6,Nangomhlaba nangaloWo Wawandlalayo
  91,7,Nangomphefulo nangaloWo Wawufezekisayo
  91,8,Waza kananjalo Wawubonisa okungawulungelanga noko kuwulungeleyo
  91,9,Inene uphumelele lowo uwuhlambululayo
  91,10,Akaphumelelanga lowo uwungcolisayo
  91,11,(Abantu) bakwaThamûd babaphikisa (abaProfeti babo) ngokugabadela kwabo
  91,12,Xa oyena mntu wayengcole kakhulu phakathi kwabo waphuma (waya kubulala imazi yenkamela)
  91,13,"Kodwa uMthunywa ka-Allâh (uSâlih) wathi kubo: “Ze nilumke! (Noyike isihelegu esiya kunihlela), yimazi yenkamela ka-Allâh le, ningayibulali okanye niyithintele ekuseleni amanzi wayo"
  91,14,"Bamphikisa ke bayibulala. Ngoko ke iNkosi yabo Yabatshabalalisa ngenxa yesono sabo, Yabenza batshabalala ngokulinganayo (abazizityebi nabangamahlwempu phakathi kwabo abangakholwayo)"
  91,15,Kwaye uAllâh Azanga Abe naloyiko lweziphumo zako oko
  92,1,Ndifunga ngobusuku xa bugubungela
  92,2,Nangemini xa ivela nokukhanya
  92,3,NangaloWo Wadala isiduna nesikhomokazi
  92,4,Inene imizamo nezenzo zenu zahlukahlukene
  92,5,"Lowo unikelayo (ngamalizo), esoyika uAllâh"
  92,6,Akholelwe kokulungileyo (kuAllâh)
  92,7,Inene Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela yokuhamba lula
  92,8,"Ke yena lowo unyolukileyo, uligogotya, ezicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni"
  92,9,Aphikisane nokulungileyo
  92,10,Siya kumenzela mpuluswa indlela eya ekungcoleni
  92,11,Kanti buza kumnceda ntoni ubutyebi bakhe xa esiya entshabalalweni
  92,12,Inene kukuThi ukunika isiKhokelo
  92,13,Yaye inene seseThu isiphelo (uBomi oBuzayo) nesiqalo (ubomi beli hlabathi)
  92,14,"Ngoko\tke\tNdinilumkisile\tngoMlilo\todwanguzayo (wesiHogo)"
  92,15,Akukho mntu uza kungena kuwo ngaphandle kosisingcoli (owala ukukholwa kwi-Islam)
  92,16,"Ophikayo, atshikile"
  92,17,"Ke bona abamoyikayo uAllâh, baya kususwa babe kude kuwo (uMlilo)"
  92,18,"Lowo\tuchitha\tubutyebi\tbakhe\tekuzongezeleleni ukuhlambuluka komphefumlo wakhe"
  92,19,Ongenzeli (kunconywa) nakuhlawulwa ngumntu
  92,20,"Ngaphandle\tkokufuna\tukukholisa\tiNkosi\tyakhe Ephakamileyo, (uAllâh)"
  92,21,Kungekudala uya kwaneliseka (xa engeniswa ePaladesi)
  93,1,Ndifunga ngesandulela semini
  93,2,Nangobusuku xa bufiphala (buzolile)
  93,3,"INkosi\tyakho\t(Muhammad)\tAyikushiyanga,\t(futhi) Ayikuchasanga"
  93,4,Inene uBomi oBuzayo bobona bulungileyo kunobu (bomi balo mhlaba)
  93,5,Yaye inene iNkosi yakho Iya kukunika (konke okulungileyo) ukuze wena waneliseke
  93,6,"Yayingakufumananga uyinkedama na, Yakunika ukhuseleko"
  93,7,"Yakufumana kananjalo ulahlekile, Yakukhokela"
  93,8,Yakufumana ulihlwempu Yakwenza isityebi
  93,9,Ngoko ke ungayiphathi kakubi inkedama
  93,10,Ungaligxothi nengqiba
  93,11,Uvakalise uBabalo lweNkosi yakho
  94,1,Asikuvulelanga1 isifuba sakho na (Muhammad)
  94,2,Sakothulela umthwalo wakho
  94,3,Obukusinda umqolo
  94,4,Saza Saphakamisa ibakala lakho
  94,5,Inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka
  94,6,"Kanti, inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka"
  94,7,Ngoko ke wakugqiba (imisebenzi yakho yosuku) zinikele kunqulo luka-Allâh
  94,8,Yaye beka iingcinga zakho zonke eNkosini yakho
  95,1,Ndifunga ngomkhiwane nangomnquma
  95,2,Nangentaba yeSinayi
  95,3,Nangesi sixeko sokhuseleko (saseMakkah)
  95,4,Inene umntu Samdala ngesona simo silungileyo
  95,5,Saphinda Samthobisela kowona mgangatho uphantsi
  95,6,"Ngaphandle\tkwabo\tbakholwayo\tbenze\timisebenzi yobulungisa. Okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongeze usilele"
  95,7,Yintoni ke emva koku enibangela ukuba niyiphike inkolo
  95,8,AyingoAllâh na Oyena Mgwebi Unobuluko kubagwebi
  96,1,Funda! Egameni leNkosi yakho Eyadalayo
  96,2,Yadala umntu ngehlwili legazi
  96,3,Funda iNkosi yakho Inesisa
  96,4,Yona Yafundisa ukubhala ngosiba
  96,5,Yamfundisa umntu oko abengakwazi
  96,6,Kodwa inene umntu uyagabadela
  96,7,Kuba uzicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni
  96,8,Inene eNkosini yakho kulapho kuza kubuyelwa khona
  96,9,Umbonile na lowo uthintela
  96,10,Umkhonzi xa ethandaza
  96,11,Ingaba umbona ekuso isiKhokelo kusini na
  96,12,Okanye uyalela (abantu) ukuba bahlonele (uAllâh)
  96,13,"Umbonile na ukuba uphika inkolo, afulathele"
  96,14,Akazi na ukuba uAllâh Uyambona
  96,15,Nakanye ukuba akayeki siya kumrhuqa ngenwele zebunzi lakhe
  96,16,(Ezo) nwele zebunzi lexoki
  96,17,Makabize koogxabakhe (bamncede) ke
  96,18,Thina Siya kubiza abagcini siHogo. (Baqubisane naye)
  96,19,"Nakanye! Ungamthobeli lowo, wena, qubuda, uzisondeze (kuAllâh)"
  97,1,Inene esi siTyhilelo Sasityhila ngoBusuku baMandla
  97,2,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba buyintoni na uBusuku baMandla
  97,3,UBusuku baMandla bungcono kuneenyanga eziliwaka
  97,4,"Ngabo kuhla iingelosi noMoya [oyiNgcwele (uJibrîl)] ngemvume ka-Allâh nemiyalelo yonke"
  97,5,(Ngobo busuku) kuba luxolo kude kube ngoms’obomvu
  98,1,Abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo babengekhe bayeke (ukuba ngabahedeni) de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo kubo
  98,2,UMthunywa ovela kuAllâh ecengceleza iziBhalo eziNgcwele
  98,3,Apho kuzo kukho iiNcwadi ezilungileyo nezithe Tye
  98,4,Kananjalo aBantu beNcwadi babengezontlaba zahlukane de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo
  98,5,"Ukanti babengayalelwanga nto yimbi ngaphandle kokukuba, banqule uAllâh, banyaniseke enkolweni yaKhe, banquleYena Yedwa, benze iSalâh (umthandazo), banikele ngeZakâh, oko ke yayiyeyona Nkolo ithe Tye"
  98,6,"Inene abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo baya kuba seMlilweni wesiHogo, ngonaphakade, bazezona zidalwa zibi"
  98,7,"Inene, ke bona abo bakholwayo, benza imisebenzi yobulungisa, bazezona zidalwa zilungileyo"
  98,8,"Umvuzo wabo oseNkosini yabo yiEdeni (uMyezo iPaladesi), ekumpompoza amanzi phantsi kwayo. Baya kuhlala apho kuyo ngonaphakade, uAllâh Uya kukholiseka ngabo nabo bakholiseke nguYe. Oko kokwabo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo"
  99,1,Xa umhlaba uNyikima ngokunyikima kwawo
  99,2,"Uze\tutyekezele\tngaphandle\twonke\tumthwalo\twawo (obungaphakathi kuwo)"
  99,3,"Abantu baya kuthi: “kwenzeka ntoni na ngawo?”"
  99,4,Ngaloo Mini uya kuchaza iindaba zawo
  99,5,Kuba iNkosi yakho Iya kuwutyhilela (okwenzekayo phezu kwawo)
  99,6,"Ngaloo Mini abantu baya kuza bengamaqela athe saa, beze kuboniswa izenzo zabo"
  99,7,"Nabani\tna\tlowo\tuthe\twenza\tisenzo\tesilungileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  99,8,"Nalowo uthe wenza isenzo esingcolileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  100,1,"Ndifunga ngamahashe agabadula, akhefuzele"
  100,2,Atakise iintlantsi zomlilo (ngamanqina awo)
  100,3,Ephumelelisa uhlaselo lwawo kwasekuseni
  100,4,Aqhumise uthuli luye kutsho emafini kusenjalo
  100,5,"Agqobhoze, aye phambili angene esazulwini (sotshaba)"
  100,6,Inene umntu (ongakholwayo) akanambulelo eNkosini yakhe (uAllâh)
  100,7,Yaye inene ulingqina lako oko (ngezenzo zakhe)
  100,8,Kwaye inene unobutyhuthu-tyhuthu ekuthandeni kwakhe ubutyebi
  100,9,Akazi na okokuba xa okusemangcwabeni kuvunjululwe kwesaa ngaphandle
  100,10,Kuze noko kusezifubeni (zabantu) kwenziwe kwaziwe
  100,11,Inene iNkosi yakho ngaloo Mini Iya kuba Isazi konke ngabo
  101,1,(IYure) yesiThonga
  101,2,Yintoni na (iYure) yesiThonga
  101,3,Kananjalo yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba iyintoni na iYure yesiThonga
  101,4,YiMini apho abantu baya kuthi saa njengamabhabhathane
  101,5,Iintaba zibe njengoboya obucazululweyo
  101,6,"Lowo\tuzenzo\tzakhe\tziya\tkufunyaniswa\tzinobunzima esikalini"
  101,7,Uya kuba sebomini obumnandi (ePaladesi)
  101,8,Ke lowo uzenzo zakhe ziya kufunyaniswa zilula esikalini
  101,9,Ikhaya lakhe liya kuba senzonzobileni (esiHogweni)
  101,10,Yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba iyintoni na inzonzobila
  101,11,NguMlilo odwanguzayo
  102,1,Ukukhuphisana ngokuwanqa ubutyebi kuyaniphambukisa (ekukhonzeni uAllâh)
  102,2,Nide niye kubekwa emangcwabeni
  102,3,Yeha! Kungekudala niza kwazi
  102,4,Kwakhona yeha! Kungekudala niza kwazi
  102,5,"Yeha! Ukuba benisazi ngolwazi oluqinisekileyo (iziphumo zokuzilibazisa ngokuqokelela ubutyebi beniya kurhoxa kuloo nto, nizixakekise ngokukhonza uAllâh)"
  102,6,Inene niza kuwubona uMlilo odwanguzayo (wesiHogo)
  102,7,"Kwakhona, niya kuwubona ngamehlo okwenyani"
  102,8,"Kananjalo\tngaloo\tMini\tniza\tkubuzwa\tngobumnandi (enabuxhamlayo)"
  103,1,Nidfunga ngexesha
  103,2,Inene umntu usekulahlekeni
  103,3,"Ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo, benza izenzo zobulungisa, bafundisane ngenyaniso, bafundisane nangomonde"
  104,1,Yeha kuye wonke (umntu) oyintlebi ohlebayo
  104,2,Oqokelele ubutyebi wabufumba
  104,3,"Ecinga\tukuba\tubutyebi\tbakhe\tbuza\tkumenza\taphile ngonaphakade"
  104,4,Nakanye! Uya kuphoswa koko kuqhawula (izinto) zibe zizicwibi
  104,5,Yintoni na enokukuchazela okokuba yintoni na eqhawula (izinto) zibe zizicwibi
  104,6,NguMlilo ka-Allâh osele uphenjiwe
  104,7,Olwatyuza uye kutsho ezintliziyweni
  104,8,Inene (uMlilo) uya kubagubungela
  104,9,uziintsika ezolulwe zande
  105,1,Awubonanga na ukuba iNkosi yakho Yenza njani na ngabanini ndlovu
  105,2,Ayizanga Ilenze liphanze na icebo labo
  105,3,Yathumela ibubu leentaka phezu kwabo
  105,4,Ezababetha ngamatye odongwe olutshisiweyo
  105,5,Yabenza banjengezala lentsimi elibhuqabhuqwe (ziinkomo)
  106,1,Ngenxa yolulanyiso lwama’Kuraysh
  106,2,Ekuwalulamiseni Senza iinqwelo zawo zorhwebo ziphume ebusika nasehlotyeni
  106,3,Ngoko ke makanqule iNkosi yalo Mzi
  106,4,"Ewondlileyo,\tYawasindisa\tendlaleni,\tYawakhusela naseloyikweni"
  107,1,Umbonile na lowo uphika inkolo
  107,2,Lowo ngulowo uphatha kakubi inkedama
  107,3,Ongakhuthazi kondliwa kwamahlwempu
  107,4,Yeha kubakhonzi
  107,5,Abangenankathalo ngemithandazo yabo
  107,6,Abanqwenela ukubonwa (ngabantu xa besenza izenzo zabo zonqulo)
  107,7,(Kodwa) besala namancedwana amancinane (eentswelo zobumelwane)
  108,1,Inene wena Sikuphe iKawthar
  108,2,"Ngoko ke thandaza eNkosini yakho, unikele (amadini) kuYo"
  108,3,Inene lowo ukuchasileyo nguye oza kunqanyulwa (angabikho alityalwe)
  109,1,"Yithi: Hini na nina bangakholwayo"
  109,2,Andikunquli oko nina nikunqulayo
  109,3,Nibe nani anikunquli oko mna ndikunqulayo
  109,4,Kanti nam andiyi kukunqula oko nina nikunqulayo
  109,5,Ukanti nani aniyi kukunqula oko mna ndikunqulayo
  109,6,Nina ninenkolo yenu nam ndinenkolo yam
  110,1,Lwakufika uNcedo luka-Allâh noloyiso
  110,2,Uze ubone abantu bengena enkolweni ka-Allâh (i-Islam) beziindimbane
  110,3,"Zukisa iNkosi yakho ke ngoko ngendumiso, ucele itarhu (kuYo). Inene Yona nguMxoleli Ohlala Esamkela inguquko"
  111,1,"Mazitshabalale zombini izandla zika-Abû Lahab, (naye) atshabalale"
  111,2,Ubutyebi bakhe nabantwana bakhe bungamncedi nganto
  111,3,Uza kutsha edangatyeni loMlilo odwanguzayo
  111,4,"Nomfazi wakhe, umthwalikazi weenkuni"
  111,5,Entanyeni yakhe uya kuqanyangelwa ngentambo yomthi wesundu
  112,1,"Yithi nguAllâh, Mnye (Jwi)"
  112,2,"UAllâh nguNaphakade, Uphelele"
  112,3,Akazali naYe Engazanga Wazalwa
  112,4,Ukanti akukho namnye ofana naYe
  113,1,"Yithi: Ndicela ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yoms’obomvu"
  113,2,Ekungcoleni kwezinto ezidaliweyo
  113,3,Ekungcoleni kobumnyama njengoko busanda
  113,4,Ekungcoleni kwabo benza ukuthakatha
  113,5,Nasekungcoleni kwalowo wenza umona njengoko esenza umona
  114,1,"Yithi: Ndicela ukhuseleko ngeNkosi yoluntu"
  114,2,UKumkani woluntu
  114,3,UThixo woluntu
  114,4,"Ekungcoleni\tkomsebezi\twokungcola\torhoxayo\t(emva kokusebeza) kwakhe"
  114,5,Lowo usebeza ezintliziyweni zoluntu
  114,6,Phakathi kweejinni naphakathi koluntu